(71, '', '&gt;From the District of Columbia, come across the Chain Bridge in NW into Va. turn right onto rte 123 Follow Chain Bridge Road up the hill and cross over GW Parkway and it turns into Dolley Madison Blvd. Follow D.M. Blvd for 5 miles to Anderson Road. Turn left onto Anderson road and drive up the hill to Commons Village on the corner of Anderson Rd. and Colshire Dr. Start will be on the side of the Safeway. Look for the wankies. &gt;From ponits North and South find your way to the intersection of the Capitol Beltway and Route 123 Dolley Madison Blvd. take exit 46B 123 North towards Mclean. On 123 North towards Mclean go to the third Traffic light which will be Anderson Road. Turn Right onto Anderson Road, follow up the hill to the Commons Village on the corner of Anderson Rd. and Colshire Dr. Start will be on the side of the Safeway. Look for the wankies. &gt;From points West, Take I66 W to the Capitol Beltway go north towards Tysons to exit 46B 123 North towards Mclean. On 123 North towards Mclean go to the third Traffic light which will be Anderson Road. Turn Right onto Anderson Road, follow up the hill to the Commons Village on the corner of Anderson Rd. and Colshire Dr. Start will be on the side of the Safeway. Look for the wankies. &gt;From out west on Route 7 Leesburg Pike head east towards Tysons Corner to the intersectiojn of 123 North towards Mclean. Follow Dolley Madison Blvd. 123 North under the Capitol Beltway then to the third traffic light past the beltway which will be Anderson Road. Turn Right onto Anderson Road, follow up the hill to the Commons Village on the corner of Anderson Rd. and Colshire Dr. Start will be on the side of the Safeway. Look for the wankies. ', 'Ledo\'s Pizza', 'Trail will be dog freindly, if it can swim... Be sure to bring dry clothes and shoes, Yes this means you too WALKERS. Oh yeah don\'t forget a flashlight! there maybe a tunnel or two or three or four... ', 'Commons Vilage Safeway 7401 Colshire Drive Mclean, va. 22101 ', ''),
(73, '', 'From DC: 1. Take I-66 West to I-495 North (toward Dulles, etc.) 2. Merge onto the Dulles Toll Road VA-267 West 3. Take Route 7 West via exit number 16 toward Leesburg 4. Turn left onto Sterling Blvd 5. Turn left onto Holly Ave 6. Turn right onto Commerce St 7. Follow to the Big Lots parking lot, look for the wankers, park &amp; hash. From Points South: 1. Take route 28 North toward Dulles. 2. Turn right onto Sterling Blvd. 3. Turn right onto Holly Ave. 4. Turn right onto Commerce St. 5. Follow to the Big Lots parking lot, look for the wankers, park &amp; hash. From Points West: 1. Take Route 7 East toward Tysons Corner 2. Turn right onto Sterling Blvd. 3. Turn left onto Holly Ave. 4. Turn right onto Commerce St. 5. Follow to the Big Lots parking lot, look for the wankers, park &amp; hash. ', 'Paid On-On-On:  The Barefoot Pelican with birthday karaoke', 'In addition to the \'600 yd trail\', a normal length trail included for no extra fee!', '', ''),
