(83, '<br />', '<!--StartFragment --><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">From Leesburg:<span>', '<span style="FONT-FAMILY: georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Bungalow Billiards</span><br style="FONT-FAMILY: georgia,times new roman,times,serif" />', '<span style="FONT-FAMILY: georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Celebrate March Madness (if you can) by wearing your favorite college garb! Of course, the hares are too cheap to provide prizes, but you should do it anyway. </span><br style="FONT-FAMILY: georgia,times new roman,times,serif" />', '<p><!--StartFragment --><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">The old PSI Net building off of Route 7 (Now part of GWU) </font></p>', ''),
