(85, '<br />', '<!--StartFragment --><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">From points south. <br /><br />1. Take 66-E to exit 53 (Route 28 North/Dulles Airport). <br />2. Go 11 miles or so and turn right onto Severn Way. <br />3. Go about a quarter mile and see the yellow hotels under construction on your left. <br />4. Turn left and zag to the right side of Sam\'s. Parking lot is in front of you. <br /><br />From points west (like, Leesburg) <br /><br />1. Take Route 7 East (Leesburg Pike) to Route 28 South. <br />2. Go 4 miles or so and turn left onto Severn Way. <br />3. Go about a quarter mile and see the yellow hotels under construction on your left. <br />4. Turn left and zag to the right side of Sam\'s. Parking lot is in front of you. <br /><br />From points east <br /><br />1. Take Rt 7 West to Sterling. <br />2. Go through Sterling and take the exit for Route 28 South. <br />3. Go 4 miles or so and turn left onto Severn Way. <br />4. Go about a quarter mile and see the yellow hotels under construction on your left. <br />5. Turn left and zag to the right side of Sam\'s. Parking lot is in front of you. </font>', '<!--StartFragment --><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">TBD, Probably Barefoot Pelican. </font>', '<!--StartFragment --><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">For those of you not up on your Shakespeare, A Midsummer Night\'s Dream takes place in the woods. This means there will be shiggy, and lots of it. There may even be a beer fairy with special treats and maybe Puck will even make an appearance. </font>', '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Off Atlantic Blvd, off to the side of Sam\'s Club parking lot. </font></p><p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><a title="Map" href="http://maps.yahoo.com/maps_result?ed=twXKhep_0TqiZYGdThsYTw8KHpa27a0YxSkYmpFoWI6S6Vvd&csz=STERLING+%2C+VA+20166&country=us&new=1&name=&qty=">Map</a></font></p>', ''),
(86, '<!--StartFragment --><span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">All this pretty weather, flowers growing, and extra daylight got you down? Okay, not us either. But join the hares anyway by wearing something blue that night. Actually, the running hares will be joined out on trail by three non-running blue hares. Find one of the little hares on trail, pick it up, and bring it to finish. You', '<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">From Centerville ', '<p><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">The Village Inn.<span>&nbsp;</span>120 E. Maple Avenue, Vienna<span>&nbsp;</span>Directions from start:<span>&nbsp;</span>Take Church to Beulah and take a LEFT on Beulah.<span>&nbsp;</span>Go to the light and make a RIGHT on Maple.<span>&nbsp;</span>Village Inn is about .5 miles down on the RIGHT.<span>&nbsp;</span>It has a black and white striped awning.</font></span></p>', '<p />', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Vienna, VA -- Behind the building complex at 501 Church St., about a block from Beulah Rd. </span><br style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" />', ''),
(106, '<span style="FONT-FAMILY: georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Sign-up begins at 6:30, hares away at 7:00</span><br style="FONT-FAMILY: georgia,times new roman,times,serif" />', '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">From pretty much anywhere, except Leesburg:</font></p><ol><li><font face="Georgia">Travel on 28 North towards Dulles Airport, go straight through the intersection of Sterling Blvd and 28. (No matter how much you feel the call of the Pelly)</font></li><li><font face="Georgia">Turn left onto Cedar Green Road</font></li><li><font face="Georgia">Follow Cedar Green about 1/2 mile and turn left onto Bryant Court</font></li><li><font face="Georgia">Bear to your right, look for wankers, park and hash</font></li></ol>', '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">As if you have to ask... The Barefoot Pelican!</font></p>', '<font face="Georgia">So I\'m f*cking this girl from behind... </font><br />', '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Diamond Tile &amp; Marble</font><br /><font face="Georgia">2854 Bryant Court</font><br /><font face="Georgia">Sterling, VA 20166</font></p>', ''),
