(94, '<br />', '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><font color="#990000">From Dulles</font>: Go 7100 south, cross over Rt 50, at second light turn right onto Fair Lakes Pkwy. Go to first light, turn right onto Fair Knoll Drive. At stopsign, turn left, then an immediate left into Malibu Grill. </font></p><p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><font color="#990000">From points south, east and west</font>. Get onto 7100 north via I-66, or not. Turn left onto Fair Lakes Pkwy (this will be the first light after I-66). Go to first light, turn right onto Fair Knoll Drive. At stop sign, turn left, then an immediate left into Malibu Grill. </font></p>', '<br />', '<br />', '<!--StartFragment --><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Malibu Grill Brazlian Steakhouse<br /><a href="http://www.mapquest.com/maps/map.adp?country=US&countryid=250&addtohistory=&searchtab=address&searchtype=address&address=4516+Fair+Knoll+Drive&city=Fairfax&state=VA&zipcode=&search=++Search++">4516 Fair Knoll Drive<br />Fairfax, VA 22033</a></font>', ''),
