(97, '<br />', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">From the beltway take Rt. 66 west to exit 52, go right on Rt. 29 to a right on Stone Rd.,</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Go approx. 1 mile to Sully Station II shopping center on the right, look for wankers in the back parking lot.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">From Sterling, Herndon area take Rt. 28 south to a right on Westfields Blvd, it will change to Poplar Tree and then to Stone Rd., take a left into Sully Station II shopping center and look for wankers in the back parking lot. </font></span></p>', '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">O\'Tooles</font></p>', '<br />', '<span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Sully Station II Shopping Center, back parking lot</font></span>', ''),
