(98, '<br />', '<font size="3"><span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">From Sterling/Herndon</span>:<br />Take 28 South.  Turn right on Westfields.  This will turn into Poplar Tree, and then Stone Road.  Right before the light at 29, turn left into the commuter lot.  Find the wankers, park and hash. <br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">From Points East (that\'s the beltway area)</span>:<br />Take I-66 West to exit 52, 29 North.  Turn right at the bottom of the ramp and take the second right into the commuter lot.  Find the wankers, park and hash.  <br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">From any other area</span>:<br />Find 29.  Then find 66.  Where they meet in Centreville,  the commuter lot is just north of 66 on the corner of 29 and Stone Rd.  <br /></span></font>', '<br />', '<br />', '<font size="3"><span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">The Commuter Lot on 29 in Centreville, VA<br />... right down the street from last week\'s start<br /></span></font>', ''),
