(116, '<br />', '<p><b>Directions from the North (Reston area)</b>:  Take the FAIRFAX COUNTY PKWY/VA-7100 South. Turn LEFT onto FAIR LAKES PKWY.  Turn RIGHT onto FAIR LAKES CIR.  End at 12501 FAIR LAKES CIR FAIRFAX VA. See Udder Ho &amp; other deviants milling about between the ballfield and the left side of Galyans. Park, hash and give Running Bare all the hell for the directions delay: he seemed to think the start was in question when he late learned that the previous hash was to be conducted in the same area. Bare\'s hashing lessons learned # 169: Never assume that your location will not be compromised by some other delirious half a half mind.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Directions from the South</b>:  Take the FAIRFAX COUNTY PKWY/VA-7100 North. Turn RIGHT onto FAIR LAKES PKWY.  Turn RIGHT onto FAIR LAKES CIR.  End at 12501 FAIR LAKES CIR FAIRFAX VA. See Udder Ho &amp; other deviants milling about between the ballfield and the left side of Galyans. Park, hash and give Running Bare all the hell for the directions delay: he seemed to think the start was in question when he late learned that the previous hash was to be conducted in the same area. Bare\'s hashing lessons learned # 169: Never assume that your location will not be compromised by some other delirious half a half mind.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Directions from the East (DC area)</b>:  Take 66 West.  Exit FAIRFAX COUNTY PKWY/VA-7100 North (toward Reston). Turn RIGHT onto FAIR LAKES PKWY.  Turn RIGHT onto FAIR LAKES CIR.  End at 12501 FAIR LAKES CIR FAIRFAX VA. See Udder Ho &amp; other deviants milling about between the ballfield and the left side of Galyans. Park, hash and give Running Bare all the hell for the directions delay: he seemed to think the start was in question when he late learned that the previous hash was to be conducted in the same area. Bare\'s hashing lessons learned # 169: Never assume that your location will not be compromised by some other delirious half a half mind.</p>', '<br />', 'Don\'t forget to:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dress for the weather</li>\r\n<li>Bring a flashlight!</li>\r\n<li>Sign up for the SH*T Halloween Hash III at <a href="http://www.sohappyhash.com/halloween3.php">the website</a> or give $11 to Cum of a Cum of a Sailor at trail!</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Galyans Sporting Goods at Fair Lakes', ''),
(103, '<font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Sign-up begins at 6:30, hares away at 7:00</font>', '<div><span class="386013400-12082004"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><font color="#990033">From Points North</font>:</font></span></div><div><span class="386013400-12082004"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Go Rt 28 south through Manassas. Turn right onto Godwin drive. Turn right into the 2nd entrance into the GMBL fields, turn left on the access road and follow it to the end. </font></span></div><div><span class="386013400-12082004"></span><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">', '<br />', 'Don\'t forget to sign up for the SHOTH camping weekend, August 27 - 29. Check the main web page (<a title="http://www.sohappyhash.com" href="/">http://www.sohappyhash.com</a>) for details!', '<!--StartFragment --><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><span class="386013400-12082004">Greater Manassas Baseball League Fields, Manassas</span> </font>', ''),
(104, '<span style="FONT-FAMILY: georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Sign-in begins at 6:30, hares away at 7:00</span><br /><span style="FONT-FAMILY: georgia,times new roman,times,serif"></span>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><b><u><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">From <place w:st="on" /><state w:st="on" />Washington</state /></place /> or points south</span></u></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">: Get to the toll road and take it to the Reston Parkway exit.<span>', '<br />', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">Keep expectations low and we won', '<font size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Around the Reston Hospital complex parking lot in <place w:st="on" />Reston</place /></font></span></font>', ''),
