(109, '<!--StartFragment --> <font face="Georgia"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Sign-in begins at 6:30, and hares away at 7:00</font></font>', '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><strong><u>From Washington or points south</u></strong>: Get to the toll road and take it to the Reston Parkway exit.  From the exit take a right and go to the 4<sup>th</sup> light (I think) and turn left onto Bowman Towne Drive.  Go through 4-way stop to the traffic light and cross over Town Center Parkway into the hospital complex.  Take the first right, drive behind the office building and look for deviants.</font></p><p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><strong><u>From 7100</u></strong>: Take 7100 Fairfax County Parkway (from either 7 or Fairfax area) toward Reston.  Take exit 606 - Baron Cameron - to Reston. Take a right onto Town Center Drive and then take your 2<sup>nd</sup> right into the hospital complex. Take another right and look for trouble.</font></p>', '<br />', '<font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">POOO tonight! Don\'t forget to bring flashlights, dry clothes, and your thirst!</font>', '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><font class="swb"><font color="#800000">Around the Reston Hospital complex parking lot in Reston</font></font></font></p>', ''),
(107, '<p><!--StartFragment --><span style="font-family: Georgia;"><font size="3">Two weeks ago', '<!--StartFragment --><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><font size="3"><strong><span style="color: red; font-family: Georgia;">From Sterling/Herndon/Reston: </span></strong><strong><span style="font-weight: normal; font-family: Georgia;">Make your way to the Beltway (I-495', '<!--StartFragment --><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"><font size="3">Grevey', '<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"><font size="3">Live trail (as usual)', '<!--StartFragment --><b><span style="font-family: Georgia;"><font size="3">At Lurie Park; Falls Church, VA<br /><br /></font></span></b><b><span style="font-size: 8pt; font-family: Georgia;">(at the intersection of Holmes Run Drive and Executive Avenue)<br /></span></b><b><span style="font-family: Georgia;"><font size="3">(ADC Map: Northern VA 15, D-09, Fac)</font></span></b>', ''),
(110, '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Sign-in begins at 6:30, and hares away at 7:00</font></p>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">From Points West</span></b><i><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">:</span></i><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><span>&nbsp;</span>66 East to Rte. 110 South to Rte. 1 South. After you come across the s-curve bridge over the railroad tracks, continue through three more lights and turn RIGHT on Wythe for one block, then RIGHT on N. Fayette for a half-block. We are the four-story brick townhouses on your RIGHT; 727 is located at the far left corner of the courtyard (end unit). <b>Please park on the street.</b></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">From Points South</span></b><i><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">:</span></i><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> Get yourself to Route 1 North, which becomes N. Patrick Street as you drive through Old Town. LEFT on Wythe for two blocks; RIGHT on <place w:st="on">N. Fayette</place> for a half-block. We are the four-story brick townhouses on your RIGHT; 727 is located at the far left corner of the courtyard (end unit). <b>Please park on the street.</b></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">From Points North</span></b><i><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">:</span></i><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"> Get yourself to 395 South, then exit GW Parkway (take the exit marked <placename w:st="on">Reagan</placename> <placename w:st="on">National</placename> <placetype w:st="on">Airport</placetype>), which becomes N. Washington St.as you enter <place w:st="on"><placename w:st="on">Old</placename> <placetype w:st="on">Town</placetype></place>. RIGHT on Wythe for five blocks, RIGHT on N. Fayette for a half-block. We are the four-story brick townhouses on your RIGHT; 727 is located at the far left corner of the courtyard (end unit). <b>Please park on the street.</b></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"></span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Or ', '<font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Founder\'s Brewery<br />607 King St., Old Town<br /><br />Hash special: $3.50 pints of house drafts!</font>', '<font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Don\'t forget to sign up for the <a href="/3legrego.php">SH*T Three-Legged Bar Crawl</a>!!</font>', '<font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Porta-Potter &amp; Dead Hare', ''),
(131, '', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">From 7 East: </span><br style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Take a\r\nright onto Dranesville road and continue through a few lights (2 or 3).\r\nTake another right onto Hiddenbrook drive, then a right on Saddlers\r\nWells drive. Look for a sign to the Hiddenbrook Pool and take that\r\nright into the parking lot.\r\n</span><br style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" />\r\n<br style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">From Fairfax: </span><br style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" />\r\n<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Take\r\n7100 North to Wiehle avenue and take a left. Follow Wiehle until you\r\nget to Dranesville then take a right. Take a left onto Hiddenbrook\r\ndrive, then a right onto Saddlers Wells drive. Look for the same pool\r\nas the wankers coming from route 7 are. Turn right into the parking\r\nlot.\r\n</span>', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">The Pelican (most likely)</span>', 'Special instructions:\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>No shukin', '<a href="http://www.splashaquatic.com/hiddenbrook_location.htm"><span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">\r\nHiddenbrook Pool\r\n</span></a><br style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" /><span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;"><font size="3"><font color="#000000">1508A\r\nSaddlers Well Drive<br />\r\nHerndon, VA 20172</font></font></span>', ''),
(129, '', '<h2>From points south & southwest</h2>\r\n\r\n<ol type="1" style="margin-top: 0in; font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" start="1"><li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Take\r\n     66-E to exit 53 (Route 28 North/Dulles Airport).<o:p /></span></li><li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Go 11\r\n     miles or so and turn right onto <st1:street w:st="on"><st1:address w:st="on">Sterling\r\n       Blvd.</st1:address></st1:street><o:p /></span></li><li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Go\r\n     about a mile and turn right by the McDonalds.<o:p /></span></li><li class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Park\r\n     in the parking lot by Big Lots, pay and hash.<o:p /></span></li></ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><o:p>', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Duh.  The Barefoot Pelican</span>', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">There will most likely be a runners trail, but if not, someone will probably lay one, like AHHB or some over-achiever.  The walkers trail will be super short.  </span>', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Big Lots\r\n</span><br style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" /><span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">300 N. Sterling Blvd. (sorta.  It', ''),
