(115, '<br />', '<span style="font-weight: bold;"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">From the North:<span style="font-weight: bold;"><br />\r\n</span></span></font></span><font size="3"><span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Take\r\n7100S.  Turn right onto Fair Lakes Pkwy.  Turn left at the fourth light\r\nonto Fair Lakes Blvd.  Go to the second light and turn left into the\r\nshopping center.  Bear right to get to the Food Lion.  Look for the\r\ndeviants.  Park and hash. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-weight: bold;">From the South:</span><br />\r\nTake 7100N.  Turn left onto Fair Lakes Pkwy.  Go to the fourth light\r\nand turn left onto Fair Lakes Blvd.  Go to the second light and turn\r\nleft into the shopping center.  Bear right to get to the Food Lion. \r\nLook for the deviants.  Park and hash.  <br /><br />\r\n</span></font>', '<br />', '<font size="3" face="Arial" color="blue" style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Bring flashlights, bug repellant and\r\na good sense of humor!</span></font>', '<font size="3"><span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Food Lion on Fair Lakes Blvd, Chantilly</span></font> <br />', ''),
(118, '<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;"><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: red;">NOVEMBER </span><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 153);">2<sup>ND</sup> </span><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: red;">ELECTION </span><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 153);">DAY <o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" class="MsoNormal"><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 153);">Are you on the RIGHT, the LEFT or just OnOn?<o:p /></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" class="MsoNormal"><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Either way it\r\nwon', '<p style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;" class="MsoNormal"><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">From the Beltway direction\r\ntake 66 towards <st1:city w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Fairfax</st1:place></st1:city>\r\nand get off at exit 57A ', 'TBD', '<br />', '<br />', ''),
(119, '<font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Sign-in begins at 6:30, hares away at 7:00.  </font>', '<p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><strong>From points South</strong>:</font></p><ul><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Fairfax County Parkway N to Spring Street exit for Herndon. (Exit is on the left)</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Right onto Spring Street (Bottom of off ramp)</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Left onto Herndon Parkway</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Left onto Van Buren.</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Right at next light into parking lot.</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Park away from the building.<br /></font><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><strong></strong></font></li></ul><p><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><strong>From Sterling</strong>:</font></p><ul><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Fairfax County Parkway S to Spring Street exit for Herndon. (Exit is on the right)</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Right onto Spring Street (Bottom of off ramp)</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Left onto Herndon Parkway</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Left onto Van Buren.</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Right at next light into parking lot.</font></li><li><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">Park away from the building.</font></li></ul>', '<br />', '<br />', '<font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif">The parking lot at 205 Van Buren Street, Herndon. That\'s on the south-west corner of the intersection of Herndon Parkway and Van Buren.</font>', ''),
(120, '<br />', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">From Sterling: <br /></span><ul><li>Take 28 South to Braddock Road East (it\'s a left -- SOUTH of 66)</li><li>Go approximately 1.5 miles.  The parking lot is on your right.</li><li>If you go past Clifton Road, you\'ve gone too far. <br /></li></ul>From points east/west:<br /><ul><li>Take I-66 to exit 53 (28 South)</li><li>Turn LEFT on Braddock Rd</li><li>Go approximately 1.5 miles.  The parking lot is on your right. <br /></li><li>If you pass Clifton Rd., you\'ve gone too far.</li></ul><br />', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">O\'Tooles</span>', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">It\'s getting cold outside -- don\'t forget to dress for the weather!  And, seriously, it\'s dark.  BRING A FLASHLIGHT!!!</span>', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Braddock Park, Centreville</span>', ''),
(121, '<br />', '<ul style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">\r\n<li>Take your most pleasing route to I-495 CAPITAL BELTWAY.\r\n</li><li>Take the VA-613/VAN DORN ST EXIT 173- toward FRANCONIA.\r\n</li><li>At traffic light T intersection turn RIGHT onto SO. VAN DORN ST.\r\n</li><li>2 traffic lights further turn LEFT onto VA-644 E. (Edison HS is on-on right).\r\n</li><li>Go straight thru two traffic lights: passing McDonalds at second T-light.\r\n</li><li>Then go 1/5 mile in center lane &amp; turn left (as road curves right) into Mark Twain MS.\r\n</li></ul>', 'King Street Blues, Kingstowne', 'Dog friendly, slight shiggy factor, could be some water to ford. BRING A FLASHLIGHT, for tunnels? Indian summer lingers but it might be cold, right?', 'Mark Twain Middle School<br />\r\n4700 FRANCONIA RD, ALEXANDRIA VA', ''),
(123, '<br />', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Take the Dulles toll road to\r\nthe Herndon/World Gate exit # 10.<span>&nbsp;</span>Take a\r\nleft onto <st1:city w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Centerville</st1:place></st1:city>\r\nroad and go through the next 3 lights.<span>&nbsp;</span>At the 4<sup>th</sup> light rake a right onto <st1:place w:st="on">Coppermine</st1:place>\r\nroad.<span>&nbsp;</span>Take the next right turn onto\r\nRiver Birch road and continue to Dulles Tech Drive.<span>&nbsp;</span>Take a right on Tech drive then take your second right turn into the\r\noffice complex.  Drive around back and\r\nlook for SH*T.<o:p /></p>', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Ned Devine\'s</span>', 'As always, bring flashlights, dry clothes, clean shoes, and pet peeves.<br />\r\nDixie -- you\'ll love this trail.<br />\r\nEverybody but Dixie -- BRING A DRY BAG.', 'Herndon', ''),
