(124, '<br />', '<b>From points South (Dulles Airport, Chantilly, Centreville) via Route 28</b><br />\r\nRoute 28 North. Take Route 7 East/Leesburg Pike. In about a mile, turn right onto Loudon Tech Drive. Bear right and you\'ll see us in the parking lot. We are across from the &quot;Border\'s Plaza&quot;. 45980 Waterview Plaza.  \r\n<p>\r\n<b>From Cascades</b><br />\r\nCascades Parkway or Algonkian Parkway to Route 7 West towards Dulles Town Center. Turn left onto onto Loudon Tech Drive. Bear right and you\'ll see us in the parking lot. We are across from the &quot;Border\'s Plaza&quot;. 45980 Waterview Plaza. \r\n</p><p>\r\n<b>From Ashburn</b><br />\r\nTake Route 7 East/Leesburg Pike. In about a mile, turn right onto Loudon Tech Drive. Bear right and you\'ll see us in the parking lot. We are across from the &quot;Border\'s Plaza&quot;. 45980 Waterview Plaza. \r\n\r\n</p><p>\r\n<b>From Reston via Dulles Toll Road (Route 267)</b><br />\r\nDulles Toll Road West to Route 28 North. Take Route 7 East/Leesburg Pike. In about a mile, turn right onto Loudon Tech Drive. Bear right and you\'ll see us in the parking lot. We are across from the &quot;Border\'s Plaza&quot;. 45980 Waterview Plaza. \r\n\r\n</p><p>\r\n<b>From Herndon via Dranesville Road (Route 228)</b><br />\r\nDranesville Road North. Take Route 7 West/Leesburg Pike. Turn left onto Loudon Tech Drive. Bear right and you\'ll see us in the parking lot. We are across from the &quot;Border\'s Plaza&quot;. 45980 Waterview Plaza. \r\n\r\n</p><p>\r\n<b>From Great Falls</b><br />\r\nGeorgetown Pike West to Route 7 West/Leesburg Pike. Turn left onto Loudon Tech Drive. Bear right and you\'ll see us in the parking lot. We are across from the &quot;Border\'s Plaza&quot;. 45980 Waterview Plaza. \r\n\r\n</p><p>\r\n<b>From the Beltway (Route 495)</b><br />\r\nDulles Toll Road West to Route 28 North. Take Route 7 East/Leesburg Pike. In about a mile, turn right onto Loudon Tech Drive. Bear right and you\'ll see us in the parking lot. We are across from the &quot;Border\'s Plaza&quot;. 45980 Waterview Plaza.<br />\r\nTake Route 7 West/Leesburg Pike. Turn left onto Loudon Tech Drive. Bear right and you\'ll see us in the parking lot. We are across from the &quot;Border\'s Plaza&quot;. 45980 Waterview Plaza <br />\r\nGeorgetown Pike West to Route 7 West/Leesburg Pike. Turn left onto Loudon Tech Drive. Bear right and you\'ll see us in the parking lot. We are across from the &quot;Border\'s Plaza&quot;. 45980 Waterview Plaza.</p>', '<br />', 'Don\'t forget that the directions above are to the Sweet Water Tavern -- go across the parking lot to get to start!\r\n<p>It\'s December!  Remember to dress for the weather, and BRING A FLASHLIGHT!!!</p>', 'Cascades area off of RT 7 in the Waterview Plaza at the opposite end of the parking lot from Sweet Water Tavern near the office buildings<br />\r\n<i>(below is directions to Sweet Water Tavern, 45980 Waterview Plaza)</i>', ''),
(127, '<br />', '<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">To get there from the north...</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Find your way to Rt 28 and drive South until you get to Rt 50.  Go\r\nWest (towards Front Royal) Immediately cut left across 3 lanes of\r\ntraffic to turn left at the first or second light (Lee Road).  Drive\r\nPast the Target and turn left in Behind it.  Look for Wankers park and\r\nhash.</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">To get there from the south...</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Find your way to Rt 28 and drive North until you get to Rt. 50. \r\nGo West (towards Front Royal) Immediately cut left across 3 lanes of\r\ntraffic to turn left at the first or second light (Lee Road).  Drive\r\nPast the Target and turn left in Behind it.  Look for Wankers park and\r\nhash.</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">From anywhere else use mapquest.com</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">14391 Chantilly Crossing Ln, Chantilly, VA</div>', '<br />', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Bring Flashlight, and change of clothes!</span>', '<span style="font-family: georgia,times new roman,times,serif;">Behind Target in Chantilly (14391 Chantilly Crossing Ln)</span>', ''),
