(167, 'If you don\'t bring a flashlight don\'t expect us to come out and lead your dumba$$ in!!<br />', '<p><font color="#cc0000"><b>From Points West (Sterling/Leesburg/Iowa)</b></font> <br />Take Route 7 (Leesburg Pike) East toward Tysons Corner. Approximately 1 mile after the Fairfax County Parkway turn left onto Georgetown Pike. Follow Georgetown Pike for approximately 1 mile and turn left onto Springvale Road. Take Springvale Road for about 1 mile and turn right onto New Ascot Drive. Park in the first available spot and look for wankers in the first yard on the left. </p><p><font color="#cc0000"><b>From Centreville/Chantilly/Fairfax</b></font> <br />Take the Fairfax county parkway to Route 7 (Leesburg Pike) and make a right onto 7 east. Approximately 1 mile after turning onto Route 7 turn left onto Georgetown Pike. Follow Georgetown Pike for approximately 1 mile and turn left onto Springvale Road. Take Springvale Road for about 1 mile and turn right onto New Ascot Drive. Park in the first available spot and look for wankers in the first yard on the left. </p><p><font color="#cc0000"><b>From Alexandria/Springfield</b></font> <br />Take Route 495 North toward Tysons Corner/Rockville. Get off 495 onto Route 7 West toward Tysons Corner/Leesburg. Follow Route 7 West for approximately 6.5-7 miles and turn right onto Springvale Road (Baron Cameron Avenue will be on your left). Take Springvale Road for about 2-2.5 miles crossing Georgetown Pike and turn right onto New Ascot Drive. Park in the first available spot and look for wankers in the first yard on the left. </p><p><font color="#cc0000"><b>From Arlington/DC</b></font> <br />Take Route 66 West toward Fairfax and get onto the Dulles access road. Exit the Dulles access road onto Route 123 (Chain Bridge Rd.) North toward McLean. Take Route 123 approximately .3 mile and turn left at the first light onto Lewinsville Road. Follow Lewinsville Road approximately 3 miles and turn right onto Route 7 (Leesburg Pike) West. Fol