(168, '', '<p><span style="COLOR: windowtext">From the North:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Take 495 South towards <city w:st="on" /><place w:st="on" />Richmond</place /></city />.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Take Exit 54A, Braddock road (VA 620) west.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span>Go 0.2 miles take immediate left at the fork in the ramp to the light (Look for the Safeway Sign).<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Cross over Braddock Road onto Port Royal Road.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Safeway is on the left behind the Exxon Mobile station.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Look for wankers.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Park and Hash.</p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">From the South:</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" /><p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="COLOR: windowtext">Take 95 North to 495 North, towards Tyson’s Corner. Take Exit 54 Braddock Road (West) A620. Cross over 495, take a left onto Port Royal Road, (Look for the Safeway Sign). Safeway is on the left behind the Exxon Mobile station.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Look for wankers.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Park and Hash.</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">From the East:</p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Take 66 West (watch HOV restrictions) to 495 South.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">    </span>Go 5.1 miles to Exit 54A, Braddock road (VA 620) west.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span>Go 0.2 miles take immediate left at the fork in the ramp to the light (Look for the Safeway Sign).<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Cross over Braddock Road onto Port Royal Road.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Safeway is on the left behind the Exxon Mobile station.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Look for wankers.<spa