(172, 'In commemoration of All Saints Day come dressed as your favorite Saint or Sinner. (Hashers and presidents by definition are sinners). There will be a prize for the best costume (selected by mismanagement - all decisions are final - and if you don\'t like it we\'ll put you on mismanagement next year).', 'Easy Way to Hash - TAKE METRO to Clarendon Metro<br />Otherwise <p><font color="#cc0000"><b>From Points West (Sterling/Leesburg/Iowa)</b></font><br />Take Route 28 to the Dulles Toll Road (Route 267) and head East toward Washington for approximately 16 miles where 267 will become I-66 East. Take I-66 East for approximately 3.5 miles and take Exit 71 - Fairfax Drive. Follow Fairfax Drive for approximately one mile and turn left onto Wilson Boulevard. **** Wilson Boulevard becomes Clarendon Boulevard at the point where the street becomes one way and at that point you will see the Clarendon Metro on your left. Turn Left onto Highland Street and park in the garage for 3033 Wilson Boulevard (Green sign for Department of Human Services). Go to the 3rd level down, look for wankers and hash. </p><p><font color="#cc0000"><b>From Centreville/Chantilly/Fairfax</b></font><br />Take I-66 East inside the beltway and take Exit 71 - Fairfax Drive. Follow Fairfax Drive for approximately one mile and turn left onto Wilson Boulevard. Follow directions after **** above. </p><p><font color="#cc0000"><b>From Alexandria/Springfield</b></font><br />Take Route 495 North toward Tysons Corner/Rockville. Get off 495 onto I-66 East and take Exit 71 - Fairfax Drive. Follow Fairfax Drive for approximately one mile and turn left onto Wilson Boulevard. Follow directions after **** above. </p><p><font color="#cc0000"><b>From DC</b></font><br />Take whatever route out of DC makes you happy and get onto Route 50 West for about 1 mile then exit onto Fairfax Drive. Follow Fairfax Drive approximately 1/2 mile, cross over Clarendon Boulevard and turn left onto Wilson Boulevard. Follow Wilson Boulevard for about 1/4 mile, turn right onto Highland Street and park in the garage at for 3033 Wilson Boulevard (Green sign for Department of Human Services). Go to the 3rd level down, look for wankers and hash. </p><p><font color="#cc0000"><b>ADC Northern Virginia Map Page 17-A3</b></font><br /></p>', 'Clare &amp; Don\'s Beach Shack 3014 North Wilson Blvd Arlington, VA 22201 (703) 465-7873', 'PI Factor - Negligible - Stroller Friendly ', 'Clarendon Metro', ''),
