(223, '<p>This is our AGM (Annual General Meeting) and the theme is the WILD WILD WEST!!!', 'Directions (super simple this time!):<br />DRIVING: From 495 exit S. Van Dorn Street. At the end of the off ramp take a left onto S. Van Dorn. Go 3/4 of a mile and take a right on S. Pickett St. Nick\'s is 0.1 mile down on your right.<br /><br />METRO: (~0.5 mile) Blue Line to Van Dorn Street Metro. Exit onto Eisenhower and take a left. Take your first right onto Metro Rd. Continue to S. Van Dorn St. and take a right. Follow S. Van Dorn St. to Pickett and take a right. Nick\'s is 0.1 mile down on the right.', 'Nick\'s Night Club: 642 S. Pickett St., Alexandria, VA <a class="inform" style="FONT-SIZE: 12px" href="javascript:popupWin(\'/app/mapping/mapPrivateEvent.do?eventId=BEYKXRHRAHYWGPZMTNKW\',\'770\',\'680\',\'yes\',\'yes\',\'no\',\'no\',\'DependentWindow\',\'no\',\'no\',\'center\')">View', '<p>A to A (of course)</p><p>Bring your Wild Wild West gear and giddyup!</p><p>If you miss trail (because you\'re doing something stupid like taking a class or r*nning a half marathon), the main party starts at 3:30 and goes til 7:30 - join us!', 'Nick\'s Night Club: 642 S. Pickett St., Alexandria, VA <a class="inform" style="FONT-SIZE: 12px" href="javascript:popupWin(\'/app/mapping/mapPrivateEvent.do?eventId=BEYKXRHRAHYWGPZMTNKW\',\'770\',\'680\',\'yes\',\'yes\',\'no\',\'no\',\'DependentWindow\',\'no\',\'no\',\'center\')">View', ''),
