(252, '<span lang="EN" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"><font size="4">It', '<p class="MsoNormal"><b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">From Webster City, Iowa (where Lube was born 30ish years ago):</span></font></b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"> Head east. Cross into Wisconsin, drop into Illinois, and then go through Indiana, Ohio, Pennsylvania and Maryland. Head south on 270 to 495 toward Northern VA/Tyson\'s Corner. At exit 47A, RIGHT towards VA-7. Keep LEFT to stay on Ramp towards Falls Church. At exit 47B, take Ramp (RIGHT) towards VA-7/ Falls Church. Go 1.2 miles. Turn RIGHT (South-West) onto Pimmit Dr (2nd to last stoplight before you cross under 66). Go to the third (I think) right and turn in (there should be a Subway on your left as you enter the parking lot). Go all the way straight back in that parking lot (up a little hill) to a hidden parking section behind the stores. Look for wankers, park and hash. Should take you about 16 hours.</span></font><font face="Georgia"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">From </span></font></b><b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Sterling</span></font></b><b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"> via Route 7:</span></font></b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"> Take Route 7 east. Cross under the beltway. Go 1.2 miles. Turn RIGHT (South-West) onto Pimmit Dr (2nd to last stoplight before you cross under 66). Go to the third (I think) right and turn in (there should be a Subway on your left as you enter the parking lot). Go all the way straight back in that parking lot (up a little hill) to a hidden parking section behind the stores. Look for wankers, park and hash.</span></font><font face="Georgia"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Cumming via the </span></font></b><b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Toll Road</span></font></b><b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">: </span></font></b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Take the exit for 495 south (outer loop). At exit 47A, turn RIGHT onto Ramp towards VA-7 / Leesburg Pike / Tysons Corner / Falls Church. Keep LEFT to stay on Ramp towards VA-7 / Leesburg Pike / Falls Church. At exit 47B, take Ramp (RIGHT) onto SR-7 [Leesburg Pike] towards VA-7 / Leesburg Pike / Falls Church. Go 1.2 miles. Turn RIGHT(South-West) onto Pimmit Dr (2nd to last stoplight before you cross under 66). Go to the third (I think) right and turn in (there should be a Subway on your left as you enter the parking lot). Go all the way straight back in that parking lot (up a little hill) to a hidden parking section behind the stores. Look for wankers, park and hash.</span></font><font face="Georgia"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><font face="Georgia" size="2"><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Cumming ', '<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"><strong>Mark\'s Pub </strong></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"><font size="4"><strong><font face="Georgia"><span lang="EN" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">2190 East Pimmit Drive</span></font><font face="Georgia"><span lang="EN" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia"