(274, '<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Courier New\'">Hey Wankers, it\'s national flower week and since we love flour we decided to celebrate. So, come dressed in your best flowery attire while you follow flour (preferably red, white, or blue flowers cause that\'s the color of flour we will be using on trail).</span> </p><p><font size="2"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Courier New">Bring a flashlight so that you may see the pretty flour.</span></font></p>', '<span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-fareast-font-family: ">Directions from points West: Take 66 or VA-267 to I-495. Go South to<br />exit 50A-B Arlington Blvd/US-50W towards <city w:st="on" /><place w:st="on" />Fairfax</place /></city />. Follow signs for<br />US-29/Merrifield/VA-650N/Gallows and merge onto Gallows Rd/VA-650 N.<br />Turn right at Lee Highway/US-29/VA 237. Look for the Safeway on your<br />right about a mile down. <street w:st="on" /><address w:st="on">West St.</address></street />will be on your left. Go to the<br />parking lot on the right side of Safeway, look for wankers, park, hash. <br /><br />Directions from points East: Get to Route 50, go West, turn right at<br />Fenwick Rd., turn right at Rogers Dr., turn right at Lee<br />Highway/US-29/VA 237. <br /><br />Directions from points North and South: Get to I-495, follow directions<br />above <br /><br />Or just click the link <br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /><br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /></span>', '<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-fareast-font-family: "><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&hl=en&geocode=&q=7279+Arlington+Blvd,+Falls+Church,+VA+22042&sll=38.875797,-77.199077&sspn=0.011493,0.019956&ie=UTF8&ll=38.871239,-77.199082&spn=0.011494,0.019956&z=16&iwloc=addr&om=1">Sign of the Whale</a></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-fareast-font-family: "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 1