(280, '<div><div class="MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><div><div class="MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">Darkness falls across the land - The 7:00 hour is close at hand<br />Hashers crawl in search of beer - To terrorize halloween this year</span></font></div></div><div><div class="MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">And whosoever shall be found - Without the soul for drinking down<br />Must stand and face the hashers of hell - or rot inside a corpses shell<br />The foulest stench is in the air - The funk of forty thousand beers<br />And grizzy hashers from every tomb - Are closing in to seal your doom<br />And though you drink to stay alive -Your body is getting hot<br />For no mere hasher can resist - The evil of the Jello Shot!!!!!</span></font></div></div><div><div class="MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"></span></font> </div></div><div><div class="MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">Come and join the Children of the night on the annual</span></font></div><div class="MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><strong>So Happy It\'s Tuesday Halloween trail &quot;Trick or Beer!!!!&quot;</strong> </span></font><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><strong>Tuesday October 30th</strong></span></font></div><div class="MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><strong></strong></span></font></div></div><div><div class="MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">Come dressed in your scariest attire as we go trick or beering thru the streets of Ballston. </span></font><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">Awards for the best costume, best couple costume, and whatever else we can think