(285, '<p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Ok, so nobody signed up for this weeks trail and after repeated attempts to beg, borrow or steal various wankers to hare the trail, the hare raiser found himself out wandering through the woods in the dark looking for suitable shiggy, tunnels and sewage drains to lay a trail through. So this week you get what is coming to you for not signing up to hare a trail with a very dry, flat, short, non-sewage tunnel, trail. </span></font></p><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Trail is A - A’/B and as you should be able to tell from who is haring, the trail will be very pleasant. Bring dogs, small children, priceless china, Nub and all your assorted breakable stuff! Just in case though, you should bring a flashlight, change of clothing, life raft, dry shoes, defibulator, and perhaps some money for taxi fare, you never know. </span></font></p><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> </span></font></p></span></font>', '<p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Arial" size="2"></span /></font><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><a href="http://maps.live.com/default.aspx?wip=2&v=2&rtp=~&FORM=MSNH#JndoZXJlMT0xNDUxK0NoYWluK0JyaWRnZStSb2FkJTJjK01jTGVhbiUyYytWQSsyMjEwMSZiYj01NC4wNTkzODc4ODY2MjM2JTdlLTQyLjA5OTYwOTM3NSU3ZTE5LjcyNTM0MjI0ODA1NzklN2UtMTEyLjMyNDIxODc1"><font color="#0000ff">Total Wine Parking Lot</font></a></span></font></p><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> </span></font></p><a href="http://maps.live.com/default.aspx?wip=2&v=2&rtp=~&FORM=MSNH#JndoZXJlMT0xNDUxK0NoYWluK0JyaWRnZStSb2FkJTJjK01jTGVhbiUyYytWQSsyMjEwMSZiYj01NC4wNTkzODc4ODY2MjM2JTdlLTQyLjA5OTYwOTM3NSU