(284, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #222222; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">It has cum to my attention that a few wankers from our mother hash OTH3 who shale remain nameless have decided that the SH*T doesn’t know sh*t about laying anything. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>My first thought…They are correct! We are half-minds and proud of it.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>But our SH*Tty GM 14K &amp; rookie Hare Raiser B$ feel otherwise. </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #222222; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">They have declared that we will go to the far corners of NOVA to HASH.</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #222222; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #222222; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Now to the point. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>The OTH’rs have an entertaining live A-B trail for the SH*T to enjoy. Others may attend but they are not to enjoy themselves.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>The hares promise the trail will be <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>3.5-4 miles long but I have no idea what the terrain will be like.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>I suggest you bring a whistle, flash light, multiple layered synthetic clothing, at least a three season tent, sports bra, &amp; a tooth brush.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #222222; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #222222; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">In closing I would like to inform you that all living beings participate in four F\'s. Food, Fight, Flight, &amp; Procreate </span></p>', '<p>King Street Metro, Basketball Court on the Commonwealth side (near the<br />townhouses).  With any luck the hares will lay trail from the metro to the start. </p><div><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">From points west/south:</span></font></p></div><div><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">95 north to 495 east (Baltimore)<br />Take the Telegraph road exit north towards Alexandria.<br />Once off the exit stay in the right lane and take the Downtown,<br />Alexandria exit onto Duke Street North<br />Make a left turn at the Second left stop light (Callahan St.), just in<br />front of the Masonic Temple<br />Go straight across King St. (Rte 7) at the next light onto Russell Road.<br />Make the 2nd right hand turn onto Rosemont Ave.<br />Make a quick right then left over Commonwealth Ave. and back up Rosemont Ave.<br />Go up Rosemont and make the right turn around the housing district.<br />Park at the end of the Culdasac, the Hash will start in the Basketball<br />Court area.</span></font></p></div><div><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"> </span></font></p></div><div><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">From the Metro:</span></font></p></div><div><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">Take the Yellow or Blue Line to King Street Metro Stop<br />Get off Metro (very important)<br />Take the Commonwealth exit from the King St. Platform, this is the<br />back exit near the Hilton Hotel, not the normal exit.<br />When you come down the stairs the Hilton will be on your left, the<br />tracks will be above you on the right.<br />Make a right under the tracks, the Basketball court will be<br />immediately to your right.</span></font></p></div><div><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"> </span></font></p></div>', '<h2><a onmousedown="function anonymous()\r\n{\r\nfunction anonymous()\r\n{\r\nfunction anonymous()\r\n{\r\nfunction anonymous()\r\n{\