(288, 'Hello and welcome to all.<br /><br />  What are you doing x-mass day??  <font size="3">Parents/ kids/ husband/ wife driving you nutz?</font><font size="4"><font size="3"> Aunt Annoy me Till I want to kill Her and her 6 rat bastards staying at your place? In the area with no family? Need some alone time with the Hash?    Perfect! This is the place for you.<br /><br />  The esteemed Hasher Humper and Spinal Tap are opening their house and combining with the So Happy Its Tuesday Hash for Trails, Traditions, cold Beer, warm food and friendly camaraderie!<br /><br />  We\'re supplying the entrees, probably turkey, ham, something vegetarian, beer, soda, water, chips, orange food, and if you\'re extra good boys and girls probably something warm to drink. You are supplying a side dish, a friendly personally and whatever else you feel like sharing.<br /><br />Cost 5$ with a side dish or something to share, $10 without <br />Start 1:30 - End 6pm-ish or on on on to the next venue<br /><br />  Please do give us yes, no, or maybe, and what you might bring, preferably by this weekend sometime so we can do our food shopping and preparing. <a href="http://www.evite.com/pages/invite/viewInvite.jsp?inviteId=GNXQCYDTSOJPLFICLWEM">Link to evite</a> Thank you.<br /><br /></font></font>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><a href="http://www.mapquest.com/maps/map.adp?searchtype=address&country=US&addtohistory=&searchtab=home&formtype=address&popflag=0&latitude=&longitude=&name=&phone=&level=&cat=&address=4101+David+Lane&city=alexandria&state=va&zipcode=">Start Trail #287</a></p>', 'TBD', '', '<p> Spinal Tap and Hasher Humper\'s House</p>', ''),
