(291, '<p>Fire in The Cornhole has discovered that he doesn\'t have to hare all of his trails near the WV stateline inorder to find the necessary amount of shiggy for a good lay.  What\'s next? Perhaps he will learn how to use the internet so he can send his directions on time.</p><p>Live A-A\' trail with all the trappings of a Fire trail, hills, water, mud, barking spiders, rabid midgets, and AHHB*. Bring a flashlight and a change of cloths as usual and remember, a warm beer is better than no beer.</p>', '  <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: 89.25pt"><a href="http://www.wmata.com/metrorail/Stations/station.cfm?station=103">Vienna/Fairfax-GMU</a></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: 89.25pt" /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><a href="http://www.mapquest.com/maps/map.adp?address=3059%20Nutley%20St&city=Fairfax&state=VA&zipcode=22031%2d1931&country=US&title=%3cb%20class%3d%22fn%20org%22%3e3059%20Nutley%20St%3c%2fb%3e%3cbr%20%2f%3e%20%3cspan%20style%3d%22display%3ainline%3bmargin%2dbottom">McDonalds</a></p>', ' Glory Days', ' ', '<p><font color="#000000"><font face="Arial">Start location is the shopping center at the corner of Nutley Street (Rt 243) and Lee Highway (Rt. 29)</font>  <span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><font size="3">We will be meeting in front of the shopping center near the Mcdonalds</font></span></font><font color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><font face="Arial" color="#000000"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 7.5pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><font face="Arial" color="#333399" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #333399; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> </span></font></span></font></span></font></p><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><font size="3">3059 Nutley Street<br />Fairfax, VA 22031<br /><br /></font></p>', ''),
(292, '<p style="BACKGROUND: white"><font face="times new roman,times,serif" color="#444444" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Live A-A trail.  Bring a flashlight and a change of clothes. Butt do not wear the nice, new long-sleeve T-shirt your mommy gave you for Christmas. Cause if someone likes it they can claim it and you <em><b><i><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">must</span></i></b></em> trade them or . . . . <strong><b><i><span style="FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">LONG</span></i></b></strong> sleeve T\'s only. \'Might be cold, so ladies wear a  . . . uh, no, . . . (come to think of it, with even my half-a-half mind, that\'s a no-brainer)  ladies do <em><b><i><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">not </span></i></b></em>concern yourself about wearing any second tier clothing. </span></font></p><p style="BACKGROUND: white"><font face="times new roman,times,serif" color="#444444" size="3"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><font color="#000000">Nick\'s is waiving the usual $5 cover charge for the guys: 20% off appetizers. </font><span class="EC_ectel"><font face="Arial" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">SHIT-kicking band starts playing at 9PM</span></font></span><font face="Arial" color="#670000" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #670000; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"></span></font></span></font></p>', '<p style="BACKGROUND: white"><font face="Arial" color="#000000" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Start location and </span></font><strong><b><font face="Times New Roman" color="#000000" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black">On-On-On:</span></font></b></strong><font face="Arial" color="#000000" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><br />is: N<span id="EC_EC_iwhomepage">ick\'s Night Club</span><span class="EC_ecstreet-address