(295, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Any SH*Tty half-mind can tell you that when Lactose isn\'t thinking about getting a piece of Asian tail he can get his shiggy on but god hates him. God shows his distain for Lactose by sending the coldest sh*ttiest weather possible whenever he hares. With any luck Just Karen\'s warm energy and Just (Chuck Norris) Wayne\'s supper human virgin strength will over power Lactose\'s sh*tty luck. </p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"> </p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Live A to A\' trail where anything goes... plan ahead wankers!!</p>', '<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">Start: McLearen Sq.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span>Herndon<br /><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span><br />From Rt 495: take Rt 267 (toll road) to exit 10,Herndon.</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">Turn left at bottom of ramp. Travel approx. 2 miles<br />and take a left onto McLearen Rd. <br />Make your first right into McLearen Sq.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Look for<br />wanker beside Bloom Grocery Store<br /><span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span><br />From Rt 66: Take Rt 28 north, exit at </span><street /></p><address><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">McLearen Rd.</span></address></street /><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "><br />Go approx. 3/4 of a mile, cross </span><street /><address><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">Centreville Rd</span></address></street /><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "><br />and turn right into<span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>McLearen Sq. Look for wankers beside<br />Bloom Grocery Store.<br />.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></span><p />', '<a onmousedown="function anonymous()\r\n{\r\nfunction anonymous()\r\n{\r\nfunction anonymous()\r\n{\r\nfunction anonymous()\r\n{\r\nfunction anonymous()\r\n{\r\nomniturePaidListingClickFire(\'1\', \'2\', \'\', \'\', \'1\', \'\');