(296, '<p>AHHB knows that he was late with the trail directions, has half-assed his co-hare recruitment, and as of Friday has not begun to scout. Not to worry, AHHB (I mean Bush) is not scared. He has assured me that he can run around in non-sensical circles for hours without getting snared. </p><p>Plan for a dark live A to B trail.  Don\'t worry, Lactose probably won\'t make it this week so the weather should be tolerable, but I would bring a change of clothes and a cash tip for the webmaster.</p>', '  <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">From the <street w:st="on" /></span></strong><strong><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"></span></strong></p><p /><address w:st="on">Dulles Toll Road</address></street />(267): <p /><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">Take the </span></strong><strong><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Reston Parkway</span></i></strong><strong><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"> (cummin from <city w:st="on" /><place w:st="on" />Sterling</place /></city />… it’s a </span></strong><strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">LEFT</span></strong><strong><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"> and cummin from Tysons… it’s a </span></strong><strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">RIGHT</span></strong><strong><span style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"> onto </span></strong><strong><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Reston Parkway</span></i></strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">) and continue on Reston Parkway</span></p></street />to the intersection with Baron Cameron Road</street />. Take a <strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Geor