(299, '<p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Do you remember the three wise men from the Bible who brought gifts to baby Jesus?  They brought stupid useless stuff like gold, frankincense and myrrh.  If baby Jesus was a hasher, they would have brought beer.  We wankers are MUCH luckier than baby Jesus - for several years we have received that glorious nectar of the gods on a weekly basis from the three not-so-wise men haring this trail (otherwise known as current and former beer bitches)!  The three wise men had a clear beacon in the night (the Christmas star) to find their destination - the pack may not be so lucky with the three not-so-wise men leading this trail.  One thing I am sure of, however, once we reach the end THERE WILL BE BEER!!!  Thank you gentlemen!  </span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Live trail (as usual)… This is a S.H.*.T. H3 trail… we hash in the shiggy and in the woods!! Cum prepared!! This is not being just being “SUGGESTED”… the hares are “WARNING”… <b><i>BRING A FLASHLIGHT!!, </i></b> whistle, and don\'t forget those green backs for the Webmaster.</span></p><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">This trail is A to A’ (that’s “A-PRIME, you wankers!!)… so that means… bring dry clothes and shoes. You may get PI (Poison Ivy)… so bring Ivy Block and a tip for the webmaster.</span></p><p class="EC_MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Oh… and don’t forget… ‘If you haven\'t done it before, maybe you shouldn\'t be doing it now’!!</span></p>', '  <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">From Sterling/Herndon/Reston (and Points West):<br /></span></strong><street w:st="on" /></p><address w:st="on"><span style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Georgia">Take <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route</i></b></span></address></street /><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal"><sp