(300, '<p><font face="Arial">Welcome to Herndon, Virginia, the perfect &quot;base camp&quot; for your visit to the Washington, D.C. Area</font><font size="1"><br /></font><font face="Arial" size="3"><b><i>&quot;Don\'t Blink or You\'ll Miss It&quot;</i></b></font> </p><p>When most people hear small town they think... boring. Not the SH*T when we stumble into a small town we think... look at all that shiggy. Well Hernon is full of it.</p><p>The hares have planned a live A to A laid back and relaxing trail. The trail is going to be so uplifting that you probably won\'t even notice the poison ivy, creeks, and sticker bushes. Just incase you should bring a whistle, flash light, ivy block, &amp; a change of cloths.  </p><p /><p> </p>', ' <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Honestly? I think if you can\'t find your own way there might be something really wrong with you, but just to be nice:</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"></span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">From Points East:</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">66 West to VA-267 W (The </span>Toll Road)</p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Take exit 10 toward Herndon</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Right at bottom of exit ramp</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Left at <street w:st="on" /></span></p><address w:st="on">Center Street</address></street /><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: