(324, '<p><img hspace="0" src="/images/fromrussiabig.jpg" align="baseline" border="0" /></p><p>SH*T-ters if you thought last week\'s trail was effed up... just wait, this trail should be just as shiggylishous. Our lovely Russians have spent a great deal of time and energy ordering AHHB into the wilds of Reston to scout this trail. </p><p>AHHB has shared a few language tips that helped him survive scouting. (To be posted after dinner &amp; a beer.)</p>', '<p class="ececmsonormal" style="MARGIN: auto 0in"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: ">(Metro)</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: "></span></p><p /><p class="ececmsonormal" style="MARGIN: auto 0in"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: ">According to the latest reports… the 11.6 mile leg of the metro to Reston will be completed by 2013, however, that is a little too late for this trail.</span></p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: "><p class="ececmsonormal" style="MARGIN: auto 0in"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: ">(Driving)</span></p><p class="ececmsonormal" style="MARGIN: auto 0in"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: ">Get yourself to the <b><i>Beltway (I-495)</i></b>. Take </span><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: ">EXIT 45</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: "> for the <b><i>Route 267, Dulles Toll Road</i></b>. Take </span><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: ">EXIT 13</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: "> for Wiehle Avenue and turn </span><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: ">RIGHT</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: "> onto <b><i>Wiehle Avenue</i></b>. Continue on Wiehle Avenue for approx., .7 miles and turn </span><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: ">RIGHT</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: "> onto <b><i>North Shore Drive</i></b>. The shopping center will be on your </span><b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: ">LEFT</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: ">. Park in front of the Fresh World grocery store in the Tall Oaks Village Center and look for wankers milling around for beer.</span></p></span>', '<p>Champ\'s American</p><p>11694 Plaza America Dr.</p><p>Reston, VA 20190</p><p>Form Start::</p><p>Turn right onto N. Shore Drive. Go to the light at Wiehle Ave. &amp; turn left. Continue on Wiehle Ave. to the light at Sunset Hills Rd. Turn right onto Sunset Hills. Continue on Sunset Hills for about .5 miles Plaza America Dr. is on the left.</p><p />', '<span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: ">Live Trail. </span>If you were at last week’s trail… then we shouldn’t have to tell you… BRING A FLASHLIGHT!!<br /><br />Miscellaneous:  As usual, bring dry clothes, and tell your virgins not to wear new shoes or clean underwear.</span>', '<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: ">Tall Oaks Village Shopping Center</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: "><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=en&q=12040+North+Shore+Drive;+Reston,+VA&um=1&ie=UTF-8&sa=X&oi=geocode_result&resnum=1&ct=title" target="_blank"><span style="COLOR: blue">12040 North Shore Drive; Reston, VA</span></a></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: "><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: ">in front of the Fresh World (formally… the Giant) grocery store in the Tall Oaks Village Shopping Center.</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #660000; FONT-FAMILY: "> </span></span></p>', ''),
(327, '', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">D-erections:</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">(Metro)</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Save gas and tolls and the environment!! Carpool!</span></i></b></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"></span><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">(Driving)</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">From </span><city /><place /><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Alexandria</span></place /></city /><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"> – 495 umm… west? Toll Road East Exit 11 (maybe….)</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">F* it. Happy searching.</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #444444; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana">Turn into that corporate park road and make a left into the parking deck depicted below that has “Start” written on it.</span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /><br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /></span></i></b></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><a href="http://maps.live.com/?v=2&encType=1&cid=AC24AF69F4B79B3C!140"><font color="#800080">Trail 326</font></a></p></p><p> </p>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="m