(330, '<p><img hspace="0" src="/images/FasterHigherStronger.png" align="baseline" border="0" /></p><p>I regret to inform you that this weeks SH*Tty hares are racists. Yes, it is true that these horney harriettes have raced over 100 miles in the last two weeks. They have competed in a 30 hour endurance race, half marathon, a 50K ultra-marathon, a ten-miler and the unnamed hare was even the FBI in a triathlon.</p><p>These rock star chica\'s are mentally prepared to kick your butts with a bad arse trail. They claim to be ready to take the pack through shiggy, creeks, billy goat paths with dangerous precipices, leech filled septic tanks, and Blair Witch Project Woods till you scream for your mommies<strong>.  </strong></p><p>What the hares are physically prepared for is a little different.  Two of the harriettes can hardly walk without ice packs and Advil and third can\'t even follow a well marked race course.</p><p>B^$ on the other hand has been checking the map and testing his skills by attempting to navigate Great Falls on an air mattress and a 6 pack.</p>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">(Metro)</b></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Not without some serious dedication but if you feel like a 4 mile run before trail Franconia Springfield is about as close as we are getting</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" /><p> </p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">(Driving)</b></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">From inside the Beltway:</b></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Get yer butt to 395 and head south</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Take exit 1B for I-95 N/I-495 E toward <city w:st="on" /><place w:st="on" />Baltimore</place /></city /></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt">Take exit 169B for <street w: