(333, '<p>Howdy SH*Tters,</p><p>Once again it is time for our favorite holiday... Halloweenie!!</p><p>This year we will be celebrating with a costume parade through Old Town Alexandria.</p><p>Sign in &amp; coolers open at 6:30, pack away at 7:30 or when we run out of hash beer.</p><p>The trail will lead to numerous shot checks and one, possibly two sh*tty bars.</p><p>Cost is $5 plus whatever you spend at the bars. Cash is faster than credit cards &amp; don\'t forget your id.</p><p>Costume contest will be judged by the hares at a special location on trail. Believe it or not we even have prizes for best costume. </p><p>The trail ends at Chadwick\'s (OnOnOn). Approximately 1 mile back to start or the metro. </p>', '<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">The pack will be gathering in Designer Bush\'s back yard. Please access the pool via the alley.</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">Click <span style="mso-fareast-font-family: "><a href="http://maps.live.com/?v=2&encType=1&cid=AC24AF69F4B79B3C!175">Start Trail #332</a> the map pin clearly shows where her back yard is. Parking is legal on the street but very limited.</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: "><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">If I was you, I would metro.  Braddock Metro is 8 blocks from Designer\'s house.</span></span></p>', '<p>Chadwick\'s </p><p>203 The Strand (near the water front)</p><p>Alexandria, VA 22314-3319</p><p>Half price burgers.</p>', '<p>A-Z walking trail relatively short. Strictly streets, alleys and sidewalks.  Possible shiggy in the form of slow-moving tourists.</p><p>Just a friendly reminder from your SH*Tty Mismanagement, even though we are starting at a hashers house, the house will not be open for us to go inside. This means that no, you can\'t go inside to put your costume on, you can\'t go inside to pee, and you can\'t go inside to grab a snack out of the fridge. So please come prepared for the weather and have your costume