(349, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Yes… that’s right… Thank God It’s February!! After two weeks of<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>put the coats away, roll-up the sleeves weather… We are bringing WINTER back for one more stint before it leaves us for another year. After all… we live here in DC. If you want sixties ~ seventies weather all year round… MOVE TO <state w:st="on" /><place w:st="on" />FLORIDA</place /></state />!!</span></p><p />', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: ">Metro…<br /></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Take Metro to the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Dunn Loring Metro Station</i></b>, in <place w:st="on" /><city w:st="on" />Merrifield</city />, <state w:st="on" />VA.</state /></place /> Catch the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">2T</span></b> bus at <time w:st="on" minute="58" hour="17" />05:58pm</time /> (to make it in time for “Bar Open”) or <time w:st="on" minute="30" hour="18" />06:30</time /> (to make it in time for start of trail).</span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: "></span></b></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: ">Driving:</span></b></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: ">From the Sterling/Herndon/Reston…<br /></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Get yourself to the </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Dulles Toll Road</i></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">(267)</i></b> heading toward the beltway. Take the exit for <street w:st="on" /></p><address w:st="on">Hunter Mill Road where you have two options.</address><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></p><p /><p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: ">Option 1:</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "> Take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">LEFT</span></b> onto </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Hunter Mill Road </i></b>until you come to the stop sign with Crowell Road. Take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">RIGHT</span></b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Crowell Road</i></b> and bear <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">RIGHT</span></b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Browns Mill Road</i></b>. Continue on Browns Mill Road until you reach Beulah Road and take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">RIGHT</span></b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Beulah Road</i></b></street />. Continue on Beulah Road</street />until you come to a stop sign and turn <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">RIGHT</span></b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Beulah Road</i></b> (that’s right… if you continue straight… you will be on Old Courthouse Road). Continue on Beulah Road</p><address w:st="on">(yes again!!) until you reach the light at Route 123, Chain Bridge Road.</address><address w:st="on">Take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">RIGHT </span></b>onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route 123, Chain Bridge Road</i></b>and then the first <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">LEFT</span></b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Branch Road</i></b>. Turn <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">LEFT</span></b> into the parking lot for the now defunct “That’s Amore”, which is just across from the street from the Giant. Park and look for wankers milling around.</address><address w:st="on"><address w:st="on"><address w:st="on"><address><address class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></address><address><address class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: ">Option 2:</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "> Take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">RIGHT</span></b> onto </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Hunter Mill Road</i></b></address><address></street />until you come to the light at Sunrise Valley Drive</street />. Take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">LEFT</span></b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Hunter Mill Road </i></b></street />(yet again… hey… I didn’t mix these up!!) and continue on Hunter Mill Road</street />until you come to the light at Lawyers Road. Turn <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">LEFT</span></b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Lawyers Road</i></b>. Continue on Lawyers Road until you come to a light at Route 123, Chain Bridge Road. </address><address>Take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">LEFT </span></b>onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route 123, Chain Bridge Road </i></b>and continue for about 5-6 blocks. Once you pass the GIANT (on your <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">RIGHT</span></b>) take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">RIGHT</span></b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Branch Road</i></b>. Turn <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">LEFT</span></b> into the parking lot for the now defunct “That’s Amore”, which is just across from the street from the Giant. Park and look for wankers milling around.</address><address><address><address><address class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: "></span></b></address><address><address class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: "></span></b></address><address class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: ">From the Beltway…<br /></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Get yourself to the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Beltway (I-495)</i></b>. Take <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">EXIT 47B-A</span></b> for the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route 7, Leesburg Pike, West</i></b>. Continue on Route 7, Leesburg Pike, West through Tysons Corner and take the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">EXIT</span></b> for <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route 123, <street w:st="on" /></i></b>toward <city w:st="on" /><place w:st="on" /><span style="COLOR: red">Vienna</span></place /></city />. Continue on Route 123, </span>Chain Bridge Road </address><address><address>Chain Bridge Road <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">(which turns into Maple Avenue)</i></b> and take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">LEFT</span></b> onto Branch Road. </address><address>Turn <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">LEFT</span></b> into the parking lot for the now defunct “That’s Amore”, which is just across from the street from the Giant. Park and look for wankers milling around.</address><address><address><address><address class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></address><address><address class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: "></span></b></address><address class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: ">Otherwise… if you’re cumming from the North:</span></b></address><address><address class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">You can take <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route 66, South</i></b> toward <city w:st="on" /><place w:st="on" /><span style="COLOR: red">Vienna</span></place /></city />. Take the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">EXIT</span></b> for </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Nutley Street</i></b></address><address w:st="on"></street /><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">…</i></b> take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: blue">RIGHT </span></b>onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Nutley Street</i></b></street /><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">… </i></b>and continue on Nutley Street </street />to Maple Avenue</street />. </address><address w:st="on">Take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLO