(350, '<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana">In typical SH*T fashion we have gone all out for this year\'s Fat Tuesday\'s trail. Some might say that we spared no expense... but that would be a lie.<br /> <br />First we started with a sizeable budget for liquid refreshments.<br /> <br />Then we got smart and recruited a Cajun, Our Own Vanna, to deliver said liquid refreshment in her very special way.<br />Vanna will be mentoring a new member to the DC hashing community, Deep Shit, in the sacred art of satisfying hashers.<br /> <br />A quote from Deep Shit, &quot;I may be young, dumb and full of shit but when I deliver the goods my customers are satisfied!&quot;  <br /> <br />Being Fat Tuesday we encourage one and all to wear apropriate Mardi Gras attire.<br /> <br />We will have Gras Beads for the boys. The girl with the most beads wins a prize.<br /> <br />Happy Hour starts at 5PM at The Front Page. Plenty of parking at the Ballston Common\'s parking garage (only $1 after 5 PM).<br /> </span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana">About The Front Page they have reserved the back bar for the hash, have lots of beads to give us, have a DJ and we get half price appetizers (except seafood) all night (5-12).</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana">For those of you that are into a little pregaming The Front Page has graciously agreed to give the hash happy hour prices on drinks until 9 PM.</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana"></span><font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#0000ff" size="6"><span style="COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: \'Comic Sans MS\'"><span>Laissez les bons temps rollez!</span></span></font><font face="Verdana" size="2"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana"><br /></span></font></p>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="georgia,times new roman,times,serif"><strong><u>From Ballston Metro:</u></strong> Walk North on N. Stafford St. until you 