(387, '<p>Bring out your inner demons, pimps, sexy pirate, giant condom or whatever you can put together from your collection of dysfunctional costumes and join the SH*T hash on a Halloween pubcrawl!</p><p><a href="/Halloween09.php">For even more details, click here!</a></p>', '<p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings"><span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #1f497d"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #1f497d"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #1f497d"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: #1f497d"><font face="times new roman,times,serif">Follow chalk from Ballston Metro to Welburn Square Park OR the alternate start if it’s raining.</font></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>', '', 'It\'s freakin Halloween, so wear a freakin costume!', '<p>Welburn Square Park – behind Qwest building at 4250 Fairfax Dr. </p><p>UNLESS IT’S RAINING – then follow the chalk to alternate start</p>', ''),
(386, '<p>Cradle and Snatch has graciously invited SH*T to a house warming party at their new home.  Weather permitting, there will be a fire pit and plenty of alcohol to help stay warm.  The location is quite unique! One minute you\'re in yuppie town and the next you\'re cruisin with MS13.</p>', '<p>Get a GPS! </p><p>From 66:</p><p>Take the exit for Glebe Rd, get on Glebe Rd towards Columbia Pike.  Make a right onto to 14st. Find parking somehow on the street. </p>', '<p>LA Bar</p><p><span jstcache="158" __jsvalues_parsed="true" jsdisplay="m.b_s!=4" jsvalues="$title:i.title;$laddr:m.laddr;$addrurl:i.addressUrl;lkgal:m.ss.lkg.addresslines;$features:features;$lkgal:m.ss.lkg.addresslines" lkgal="undefined"> </span><span style="DISPLAY: none" jstcache="159" jsdisplay="m.b_s==4&&i.realestate_data" jsvalues=".innerHTML:i.realestate_data.attr_html"></span></p><div class="phone" jstcache="143" __jsvalues_parsed="true" jsvalues="$type:$this.type" jsinstance="*0" jsselect="i.phones"><span class="tel" dir="ltr" jstcache="160" jscontent="$this.number">(703) 685-1560</span><span class="type" style="DISPLAY: none" jstcache="161" jsdisplay="$type" jscontent="\' - \'+$type"></span></div><div style="DISPLAY: none" jstcache="144" jsdisplay="i.transitSchedules && i.transitSchedules.line_groups" jsvalues="$canMaximize:i.maxUrl || \'\'; $isMaximized:false"><span jstcache="162" jsvalues="$iwIsDetailed:$this.iwIsDetailed" jsselect="i.transitSchedules"><div class="tsch" jstcache="178" jsdisplay="!$iwIsDetailed"><div jstcache="189" transclude="tsch_linediv"></div></div><div class="tsch" jstcache="179" jsdisplay="$iwIsDetailed"><div jstcache="190" transclude="tsch_detlinediv"></div></div><table width="96%" jstcache="180" jsdisplay="hasApprox"><tbody jstcache="0"><tr jstcache="0"><td class="tsapprox" jstcache="0"></td></tr></tbody></table></span></div><div class="tsch" style="DISPLAY: none" jstcache="145" jsdisplay="i.transitSchedules && i.transitSchedules.stopCodeStr"><span jstcache="163" j