(388, ' Great Falls?', '<p>  <strong>From Fairfax:</strong> 7100 north and turn right on Route 606 (Baron Cameron Ave). Continue onto <strong>Springvale Rd/<wbr />State Route 674. </strong>Turn <strong>right</strong> at <strong>New Ascot Dr. Look for the Gazebo downhill by the pond.</strong></p><p><strong>From Tysons Corner: </strong>Dulles Toll Road 267 West (or Route 7 North if you\'re too cheap). Take exit for 674 (Hunter Mill Rd.) and make a right. Turn right on Route 606 (Baron Cameron Ave). Continue onto <strong>Springvale Rd/<wbr />State Route 674. </strong>Turn <strong>right</strong> at <strong>New Ascot Dr. Look for the Gazebo downhill by the pond.</strong></p><p />', 'Old Brogue Irish Pub<br />760 Walker Rd<br />Great Falls, VA 22066<br />', '<p>Bring the usual stuff, a flashlight and dry clothes.</p><p>OnOnOn Specials:</p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">SPECIALS: (With thanks to legendary hasher and owner of the Brogue, &quot;Drinks On Me, Bud&quot;)<br /> <br />BEER:<br /> <br />Yeungling  Pitchers  $9.99  (normally $16.50)<br />Blue Moon Pitchers  $9.99  (Normally $15.50)<br />Miller Lite Pitchers   $9.99  (Normally $12.50)<br /> <br />Nacho Platters $5.00<br /> <br />Italian Dinner $10.95</span><br /><br /></p>', '<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?ie=UTF8&hl=en&msa=0&msid=114946079815076584162.0004773c48e015fe0a2cb&ll=39.005979,-77.293282&spn=0.024545,0.054502&t=h&z=14&iwloc=0004773c4f1f23d11594a">Trail 387</a><br />The Gazebo located next to the pond downhill from the following address<br />10440 New Ascot Dr.<br />Great Falls VA 22066<br />DO NOT GO TO THE HOUSE, OR PISS IN THE YARD. GO DIRECTLY TO THE GAZEBO.<br />', ''),
(389, 'It\'s the Marine Corps birthday and you\'re invited to the celebration!  Come in your best camo outfit and gear, cause we may have to be in formation the entire time while we look for Charlie\'s in the Rosslyn area.  If you don\'t do it for the beer, then do it for your country! Remember, no one gets left behind except for No Child.', '<p>Metro: Take the metro to Rosslyn, RUN UP the escalator follow the chalk to start. </p><p>From the West: 66 to Exit 75 for Rosslyn.  First light you will hit is N. Nash St. You can turn Right and park on the street since there are typically plenty of spots on this road.</p>', '<p>Rhodeside Grill:</p><p><span jsvalues="$title:i.title;$laddr:m.laddr;$addrurl:i.addressUrl;lkgal:m.ss.lkg.addresslines;$features:features;$lkgal:m.ss.lkg.addresslines" jsdisplay="m.b_s!=4" jstcache="124" __jsvalues_parsed="true" lkgal="undefined"> </span><span style="DISPLAY: none" jsvalues=".innerHTML:i.realestate_data.attr_html" jsdisplay="m.b_s==4&&i.realestate_data" jstcache="125"></span></p><div class="phone" jsvalues="$type:$this.type" jsselect="i.phones" jstcache="109" jsinstance="*0" __jsvalues_parsed="true"><span class="tel" dir="ltr" jscontent="$this.number" jstcache="126">(703) 243-0145</span><span class="type" style="DISPLAY: none" jsdisplay="$type" jscontent="\' - \'+$type" jstcache="127"></span></div><div style="DISPLAY: none" jsvalues="$canMaximize:i.maxUrl || \'\'; $isMaximized:false" jsdisplay="i.transitSchedules && i.transitSchedules.line_groups" jstcache="110"><span jsvalues="$iwIsDetailed:$this.iwIsDetailed" jsselect="i.transitSchedules" jstcache="128"><div class="tsch" jsdisplay="!$iwIsDetailed" jstcache="144"><div jstcache="155" transclude="tsch_linediv"></div></div><div class="tsch" jsdisplay="$iwIsDetailed" jstcache="145"><div jstcache="156" transclude="tsch_detlinediv"></div></div></span></div><span id="iwhomepage" jsvalues="lkgurl:(m.ss.lkghp?m.ss.lkg.hp.actual_url:m.ss.lkg.hp);lkgdomain:(m.ss.lkg.hp?m.ss.lkg.hp.domain:null)