(425, '<p>Our very own Tikki Tooki Blah blah blah is leaving to lead a less exciting life as a Potato farmer out West. </p>', '<p>Automobile </p><p>From the East: Take 66 to exit 57A onto Rt50, get on the right lane and make a right onto Waples Mill road. Go 0.2miles and make a right onto Government Center Pkwy. Go 1.4 miles and you\'ll see the school bus depot on your right. Turn into the lot and look for Wankers milling about.</p><p>From the West: Take 66 to exit 55, 7100 towards Herndon.  Go 1 mile and make a right onto Fairfax Lakes Pkwy.  Go 1 mile and make a right onto Monument Drive, then turn right onto Government center pkwy after going over the 66 overpass.  Make your first available left into the school bus depot.  Look for wankers milling about.</p>', '<p>Blue Iguana</p><p><span jsdisplay="m.b_s!=4" jsvalues="$title:i.title;$laddr:m.laddr;$addrurl:i.addressUrl;$features:features" __jsproperties_parsed="true" jstcache="113"> </span><span style="DISPLAY: none" jsdisplay="m.b_s==4&&i.realestate_data" jsvalues="innerHTML:i.realestate_data.attr_html" jstcache="114"></span></p><div class="phone" jsvalues="$type:$this.type;$mobile:!!$features.mobile" __jsproperties_parsed="true" jstcache="99" jsselect="i.phones" jsinstance="*0"><span dir="ltr" jsdisplay="!$mobile" jstcache="115" jscontent="$this.number">(703) 502-9877</span></div><p /><div jsvalues="$addrline:$this;" __jsproperties_parsed="true" jstcache="128" jsselect="i.addressLines" jsinstance="0"><span dir="ltr" jsdisplay="$title||!$laddr||!$addrurl" jsvalues="innerHTML:$addrline;dir:bidiDir($addrline,true)" __jsproperties_parsed="true" jstcache="135">12727 Shoppes Lane</span><a style="DISPLAY: none; TEXT-DECORATION: underline" target="_parent" jsdisplay="$features.embed&&!$title&&$laddr&&$addrurl" jsvalues="href:$addrurl" jstcache="136"><span jsvalues="innerHTML:$addrline;dir:bidiDir($addrline,true)" jstcache="138"></span></a></div><div jsvalues="$addrline:$this;" __jsproperties_parsed="true" jstcache="128