(485, '<p>Now… what is so special about August 30th you ask?</p><p>Well… I’m glad you asked!! On this day we will be mourning the death of Michael Jackson. Errr… no… not THAT Michael Jackson!!</p><p>Michael Jackson (27 March 1942 – 30 August 2007) was an English writer and journalist. He was the author of several influential books about beer and whisky. Michael Jackson became famous in beer circles in 1977 when his book The World Guide To Beer was published. This was later translated into more than ten languages and is still considered to be one of the most fundamental books on the subject.</p><p>So… anyone that can write “influential” books about BEER has to be honored by none other than… The Hashers!!</p><p />', '<p><table style="WIDTH: 100%" id="yui_3_2_0_5_1314362431766185" class="yiv1320214734MsoNormalTable" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tbody id="yui_3_2_0_5_1314362431766184"><tr id="yui_3_2_0_5_1314362431766200"><td style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0in; PADDING-LEFT: 0in; PADDING-RIGHT: 0in; PADDING-TOP: 0in" id="yui_3_2_0_5_1314362431766199"><p id="yui_3_2_0_5_1314362431766198" class="yiv1320214734MsoNormal"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: \'serif\'">From Sterling: </span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: \'serif\'">You’re there!!</span></p><p class="yiv1320214734MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: \'serif\'"> </span></p><p id="yui_3_2_0_5_1314362431766218" class="yiv1320214734MsoNormal"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: \'serif\'">From I-495:</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: \'serif\'" id="yui_3_2_0_5_1314362431766216"> Find your way to: <b>I-495: </b>Take <b>EXIT 45A</b> to merge onto the <b><i>Dulles Toll Road/VA-267</i></b> towards Reston/Herndon/Sterling (donate your pre-lube beer money to the toll booths). Continue on the Dulles Toll Road for approx. 12.0 miles and take <b>EXIT 9B</b> for <b><i>VA-28 North/Sully Road</i></b> (donate more beer money to the toll booth). Continue on VA-28/Sully Road for approx. 4.5 miles and take the <b>EXIT</b> 