(472, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Seeing that it’s a White House Hash House Harriers (WH4) Trail… then it MUST BE “Metro Accessible” (sort of… it’s just not THERE YET)!!<p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: black; font-size: 19pt;">Tysons East Station<p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2.25pt 0in 3.75pt;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: black; font-size: 10pt;"><a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/tysons_east_rendering_5.jpg" title="Tysons East - Exterior Rendering"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">View an online slideshow with the latest station information »</span></a> <a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/tysons_east_rendering_6.jpg" title="Tysons East - Platform Rendering"></a><a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/CapitalOne1.jpg" title="Tysons East - Photograph of existing area surrounding new station"></a><a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/CapitalOne2.jpg" title="Tysons East - Photograph of existing area surrounding new station"></a><a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/MITRE.jpg" title="Tysons East - Photograph of existing area surrounding new station"></a><a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/NorthropGrumman.jpg" title="Tysons East - Photograph of existing area surrounding new station"></a><a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/east_rendering.gif" title="Tysons East - Arial Rendering"></a><a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/siteplan.jpg" title="Tysons East - Site Plan"></a><a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/tysons_arial.jpg" title="Tysons East - Arial View"></a><a href="http://www.dullesmetro.com/stations/images/TysonsEast/TysonsStations.gif" title="Tysons East - Map"></a><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2.25pt 0in 3.75pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;">Location:</span></b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;"> on Route 123 at <street w:st="on"><address w:st="on">Scotts Crossing Road/Colshire Drive</address></street><p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2.25pt 0in 3.75pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;">Type of Station:</span></b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;"> Aerial<p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2.25pt 0in 3.75pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;">Station Facilities:</span></b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;"> <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 1.5pt 22.5pt 1.5pt 15pt;"><span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;"><span><img height="12" width="12" src="PicExportError" alt="*" /><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt;">2 station entrances (each side of Route 123) <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 1.5pt 22.5pt 1.5pt 15pt;"><span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;"><span><img height="12" width="12" src="PicExportError" alt="*" /><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt;">Pedestrian bridge crossing Route 123 <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 1.5pt 22.5pt 1.5pt 15pt;"><span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;"><span><img height="12" width="12" src="PicExportError" alt="*" /><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt;">Bus dropoff/pickup <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 1.5pt 22.5pt 1.5pt 15pt;"><span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;"><span><img height="12" width="12" src="PicExportError" alt="*" /><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt;">Kiss &amp; Ride <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2.25pt 0in 3.75pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;">Platform Height (approx.):</span></b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;"> <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 1.5pt 22.5pt 1.5pt 15pt;"><span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;"><span><img height="12" width="12" src="PicExportError" alt="*" /><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt;">East/Inbound End: 53\' <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 1.5pt 22.5pt 1.5pt 15pt;"><span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;"><span><img height="12" width="12" src="PicExportError" alt="*" /><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt;">West/Outbound End: 35\' <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 1.5pt 22.5pt 1.5pt 15pt;"><span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;"><span><img height="12" width="12" src="PicExportError" alt="*" /><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt;">Average: 44\' <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2.25pt 0in 3.75pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;">Mezzanine Height (approx.):</span></b><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: black; font-size: 11pt;"> <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 1.5pt 22.5pt 1.5pt 15pt;"><span style="font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;"><span><img height="12" width="12" src="PicExportError" alt="*" /><span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt;">East/Inbound End: 32\' <p /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-inden