(477, '<p>If ya had fun on the 4th, this is gonna be a blast too.... A <strike>treasure hunt</strike> flour hunt of epic proportions! Yes, we will once again search the woods of Herdon for hours for sparse puffs of flour, and not make it to the bar before it closes!</p>', '<span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: "><p class="MsoPlainText" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Consolas" size="3">From Fairfax County Parkway:</font></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><font face="Consolas"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">        </span>Take the exit for for Elden, and go West</font></font></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><font face="Consolas"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">        </span>Turn right at Herndon Parkway</font></font></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><font face="Consolas"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">     </span><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span>Turn right at 415 Queens Row St onto Hunters Creek Pool Rd (It looks like a driveway)</font></font></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Consolas" size="3">***Find wankers and park***</font></p></span>', '  <span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">Carpool: 208 Elden Street #100, Herndon, VA (571) 203-7995</span>', '<p class="MsoPlainText" style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><font face="Consolas">Trail will be A-B, and include a few nice checks.</font></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">*Bring a complete change of dry clothes, as they will be needed. Bring water wings, tubes, or maybe even a small raft. Seriously, bring a fucking raft. Heavy shiggy, Not dog, stroller, or really even wanker friendly.</span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">BierMeister: TBD</span></p>', '<p><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=200158719398624397366.000494a68690da6d26b01&msa=0&ll=38.968518,-77.362418&spn=0.030931,0.0418">Trail 476</a></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">Runnymede Park, on Hunters Creek Pool Rd (not the park entrance directly off of Herndon Parkway.)</span></p>', ''),
(481, '<p>America might default on their debt today; will the Matt\'s default on trail! Write to your representatives, and don\'t let the default happen!!!</p>', '&nbsp;', '<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; ">Kalypso\'s Sports Tavern</span><div id="yui_3_2_0_5_131214257951689" style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; "><span class="yiv484144057Apple-style-span" id="yui_3_2_0_5_131214257951686" style="border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 15px; font-family: arial, sans-serif; ">1617 Washington Plz<br />Reston, VA 20190-4305</span></div>', '<p>BeirMiester: SheFingeredMe</p>', '<p><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?msid=200158719398624397366.0004a96302b810c882af1&msa=0&ll=38.959676,-77.333021&spn=0.033771,0.059738&t=h&z=14">Trail 480</a></p><p><div style="border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; ">This is behind</div><div id="yui_3_2_0_5_131214257951680" style="border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; "><span class="yiv484144057Apple-style-span" id="yui_3_2_0_5_131214257951677" style="border-collapse: collapse; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; "><div id="yui_3_2_0_5_131214257951674" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><span dir="ltr" id="yui_3_2_0_5_131214257951671">1800 Michael Faraday Court</span></div><div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><span dir="ltr">Reston, VA 20190-5303</span></div><div><span dir="ltr"><br /></span></div></span></div></p>', ''),
(479, 'Bacon Day hash? Does that mean Bacon infused Martini\'s and Bacon Bloody Mary\'s???', '&nbsp;', '<p>Possibly- A Taste of the World</p><p><a href="http://www.atasteoftheworld.net/">http://www.atasteoftheworld.net/</a></p>', '<p>Don\'t dress like a sloppy a$$-hat at A Taste of the World!</p>', '<p><a title="Trail 479" href="http://maps.google.com/maps?msid=200158719398624397366.0004a81bd4c1785bb7ad0&msa=0&ll=38.95477,-77.378061&spn=0.015468,0.0209&t=h&z=16">Trail 479</a></p><p><span style="font-size: 11pt; ">251 Sunset Park Drive, Herndon, VA 20170-5220</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(484, '<p>Somebody else sign up to hare so we don\'t have to keep running these AWESOME trails!</p>', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">~From the south:</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Go north (choose a road, Reston Parkway or Fairfax County Parkway are two good ones)</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Turn right onto Wiehle Ave</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Turn Right onto North Villiage Rd.</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Pool is on the left</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">~From the east:</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Take Rt 7 west</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Turn left onto Reston Parkway</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Turn left onto Wiehle Ave</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Turn Right onto North Villiage Rd.</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Pool is on the left</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">~From the west</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Take Rt 7 east</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: ">Turn right onto Reston Parkway</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span