(500, '<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Dear SHIT HASHER…</span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"></span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">In merit that I am no longer “Just Gail”, “Suckled to B” has succumbed to the peer pressure of Thanksgiving to “put out” my virginity S.H.*.T. Trail: The “Feral Turkey Trot” Trail.</span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"></span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Be gentle while playing with my feral p*ssies at the “Shot Check”!!</span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"></span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Be sure to drink every drop @ the “Beer Check” so that clean-up is made easy =}~ A wise (?) yet dear (dead) alcoholic once said to me… “don’t waste good booze…”</span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"></span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">In honor of<span>&nbsp;</span>wing night, bring your WING man (woman) to help discharge your pinned up ammunition somewhere between the “START” and “FINISH” behind Shooter McGee’s.</span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 12pt;">&gt;o=&lt;))</span></p>', '<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: Georgia;">FROM <place w:st="on"><city w:st="on">STERLING</city></place>:</span></b><span style="font-family: Georgia;"> Find your way to the Beltway (that was easy!!)…</span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"></span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: Georgia;">FROM I-495 (Beltway):<br /></span></b><b><i><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Take I-395 North</span></i></b><span style="font-family: Georgia;"> toward DC. Take the <b>EXIT</b> for <b><i>Route 236, East / <street w:st="on" /></i></b>toward Landmark. Turn <b>LEFT</b> onto </span>Duke Street <b><i>N. Paxton Street </i></b>and take your immediate <b>RIGHT</b> onto the service road. After you pass the drive-in for McDonalds… turn <b>LEFT</b> into the parking lot and proceed to the rear of the buildings. Park and look for wankers milling around.</p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"></span></p><p /><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">If you are coming the other direction on </span>Duke Street… you can get to the same service road at <street w:st="on" /></p><address w:st="on">N. Pickett Street </address>', '<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Shooter McGee’s </span></p><p /><p /><address w:st="on"><street w:st="on"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">5239 Duke Street</span></street><br /><city w:st="on"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Alexandria</span></city><span style="font-family: Georgia;">, <state w:st="on">VA</state> <postalcode w:st="on">22304</postalcode></span></address><span style="font-family: Georgia;">703.751.9266<p /><p><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Directions to the OnOnOn: WALK to the FRONT parking lot!!</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia; font-size: 12pt;">Specials: It’s WING NIGHT at Shooter McGee’s and they will have a live band after 09:00pm</span> </p></span>', '<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Final Disclaimer:</span></b><span style="font-family: Georgia;"> Bring dry clothes and shoes, bug spray, sunscreen (NOT!!), condoms (as always… be safe!!), your grandmother’s underwear (why… we don’t know. Hummm… or is it… you never know?), and your appetite for some fine beers from all over the world!! And… finally… should we remind you… shiggy-socks and/or PI Block.</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(102, 0, 0);"><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=en&q=5255+Duke+Street,+Alexandria,+VA&gs_upl=2536l2536l0l3975l1l1l0l0l0l0l84l84l1l1l0&bav=on.2,or.r_gc.r_pw.,cf.osb&biw=1600&bih=754&wrapid=tlif132164821901110&um=1&ie=UTF-8&hq=&hnear=0x89b7b23527c59fff:0x4e42fb2e1f577e28,5255+Duke+St,+Alexandria,+VA+22304&gl=us&ei=X8DGTtWfC8ru0gGLsaUf&sa=X&oi=geocode_result&ct=title&resnum=1&ved=0CBsQ8gEwAA"><font color="#0000ff">Trail#499</font></a></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(102, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;">Parking lot behind Landmark Quest Diagnostics (next to Shooter McGee’s): <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=en&q=5255+Duke+Street,+Alexandria,+VA&gs_upl=2536l2536l0l3975l1l1l0l0l0l0l84l84l1l1l0&bav=on.2,or.r_gc.r_pw.,cf.osb&biw=1600&bih=754&wrapid=tlif132164821901110&um=1&ie=UTF-8&hq=&hnear=0x89b7b23527c59fff:0x4e42fb2e1f577e28,5255+Duke+St,+Alexandria,+VA+22304&gl=us&ei=X8DGTtWfC8ru0gGLsaUf&sa=X&oi=geocode_result&ct=title&resnum=1&ved=0CBsQ8gEwAA"><font color="#0000ff">5255 Duke Street</font></a>, <city w:st="on">Alexandria</city>, <state w:st="on">VA</state><span>&nbsp;</span><postalcode w:st="on">22304</postalcode>.</span> </p>', ''),
(501, '<span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">I was working on my crossword puzzles the other day in my favorite library (you know… the one with the ‘white’ chair, BIG HOLE?) anyway… Puzzle 17 ~ 51 Across ~ “(blank) and hounds (outdoor game).<br /><br />Any guesses?<br /><br />That’s RIGHT!!<br /><br />So… it obviously <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">MUST</b> be a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">SIGN!!</b> The So Happy It’s Tuesday Hash House Harriers 500<sup>th</sup> Trail!! AND… this is really… SH*T H3’s 500!! Unlike OTHER kennels that have 1,399¼, 1,399½, 1,399¾, 1,399<sup>7/8</sup></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">… 1400<sup>th</sup>!! (opps… did I say that out loud?)<br /><br />So… cum out to SH*T H3’s 500<sup>th</sup>… contribute $5.00 and get <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">NOTHING</b> but a Shitty Trail and BEER!! Oh… and we have some nice haberdashery items that just came in!!<br /><br />See… “Momma Told Me…” for details!!</span></span></p></span>', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">FROM VIENNA METRO:</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "> <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">EXIT</b> the metro station to the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">RIGHT</b> towards <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Saintsbury Drive</i></b>. Take a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">LEFT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Saintsbury Drive</i></b> and then a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">RIGHT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Nutley Street</i></b>. Continue on <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Nutley Street</i></b> and cross over Route 29, Lee Highway and “head” to the shopping center on your left. Go past Glory Days / Micro Center to the parking lot in the upper, rear corner (It’s a total of 0.7 miles from metro).</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">FROM STERLING/HERNDON/RESTON:</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "> Take <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route 267, Dulles Toll Road</i></b> and take the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">EXIT</b> for <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Hunter Mill Road</i></b>. Turn <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">RIGHT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Hunter Mill Road</i></b> and then a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">LEFT</b> on <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Hunter Mill Road</i></b>. Continue on <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Hunter Mill Road</i></b> for approx. 1.8 miles and turn <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">LEFT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Lawyers Road</i></b>. Continue on <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Lawyers Road</i></b> and cross over Route 123 onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Courthouse Road</i></b>. Continue on <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Courthouse Road</i></b> and turn <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">LEFT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Nutley Street</i></b>. Continue on <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Nutley Street</i></b> past the Vienna Metro (picking up wankers on the way) and cross over Route 29, Lee Highway. The Pan Am Shopping Center will be on your <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">LEFT</b>. “Head” behind Micro Center to the upper parking lot in the corner. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>Park and look for wankers milling around.</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">FROM I-495 (Beltway): </span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Take <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">EXIT 50A</b> for <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">U.S. Route 50, West</i></b> towards Fairfax. Continue on <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">U.S. Route 50, West</i></b> for approx. 2.3 miles and turn <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">RIGHT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Nutley Street</i></b>. The Pan Am Shopping Center will be on your <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">RIGHT</b> before you get to Route 29, Lee Highway. “Head” behind Micro Center to the upper parking lot in the corner. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span>Park and look for wankers milling around.</span></p><p /><p> </p><p /><p> </p>', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><a href="http://www.glorydaysgrill.com/"><font color="#0000ff">Glory Days Bar &amp; Grill</font></a> (Pan Am Shopping Center)</span></p><p /><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=en&cp=35&gs_id=2&xhr=t&q=3059+nutley+street+fairfax+va+22031&gs_upl=&bav=on.2,or.r_gc.r_pw.,cf.osb&biw=1920&bih=899&wrapid=tljp132231855548600&um=1&ie=UTF-8&hq=&hnear=0x89b64b8a859f8f5f:0xca99d4ef2e03e6e4,3059+Nutley+St,+Fairfax,+VA+22031&gl=us&ei=0_rQToTNIMje0Q