(530, '<span style="FONT-FAMILY: \'Georgia\',\'serif\'; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes"><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Greetings!<br /><br />Don\'t let today\'s weather scare you away from trail tonight.  It should be a crazy good time.  AND a (mostly) covered finish where we won\'t even need Red Solo Cups!<br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /><br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /></span></p><p /><div style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 1pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0in; PADDING-RIGHT: 0in; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: medium none; PADDING-TOP: 0in; mso-element: para-border-div; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt"><p style="BORDER-BOTTOM: medium none; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0in; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0in; PADDING-RIGHT: 0in; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: medium none; PADDING-TOP: 0in; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .75pt; mso-padding-alt: 0in 0in 1.0pt 0in" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Hope to see you there!<br />CJ<br /><br />P.S.: If everyone is soaking wet at the end, CJ might set up a &quot;ghetto&quot; slip and slide....maybe.  Might.  Maybe.  If you\'re nice.  If I like you.<br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /><br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /></span></p><p /></div><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">WHEN: Tuesday June 12<sup>th</sup>, 2012: Sign-In at 6:30pm, Hares Away at 7:00pm,<br />Pack Away at 7:15pm<br /><br />HOW MUCH: 5 dolla make you holla!</span></p></p><p> </p></span>', '<span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span><strong>From Sterling/Herndon/Reston: </strong>Find Sterling Blvd.<br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /><br style="mso-special-character: line-break" /></span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Continue on Sterling Blvd. for approximately 1.5 miles<br />Turn Right onto E Holly Ave. <br />Take first Right onto Commerce St.<br />Take next Right onto Enterprise.<br />Continue straight on Enterprise Dr. directly into parking lot for library.<br />Look for Hashers cowering in back corner.</span></p><p /><p><span><strong>From I-495:</strong> (For a non-toll option google route using Rt. 7)</span></p><p /><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Find your way to the Beltway: Take EXIT 45A for VA 267 West / Dulles<br />Toll Road toward Dulles Airport. Continue through the main tolls and continue <br />on the Dulles Toll Road for approx. 8 miles to EXIT 9B for Sully Rd (VA-28N) <br />Continue on 28N for approx. 2 miles and take the exit State Rt. 846/Sterling Blvd S.</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Continue on Sterling Blvd. for approximately 1.5 miles<br />Turn Right onto E Holly Ave. <br />Take first Right onto Commerce St.<br />Take next Right onto Enterprise.<br />Continue straight on Enterprise Dr. directly into parking lot for library.<br />Look for Hashers cowering in back corner.</span></p></span>', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">TBD</span></b></p>', '', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><a href="/my_hare.php?hshr_id=80&hare_count=124"><font color="#0000ff">Trail#531</font></a></span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Back parking lot behind Long &amp; Foster: <a href="/my_hare.php?hshr_id=80&hare_count=124"><font color="#0000ff">6862 Elm Street, McLean, VA</font></a></span> </p>', ''),
(532, '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Okay… the ‘Tour’ is over… how many trails did some of you wankers manage to make? I know I saw some old-timers out there. “Fire in the CornHole” for a several trails… “Wookin’ Pa Nub” for a few!!</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Maybe NEXT YEAR… we make a statement on the number of S.H.*.T.ers in attendence!!</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">OnOn… </span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Bush</span></p>', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">From Sterling/Herndon/Reston: </span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Take <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Dulles Toll Road/VA-267</i></b> (or save a few dollars on tolls and take U.S. Route 7, East) towards <span style="COLOR: red">Tysons Corner</span>. Take the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">EXIT</b> for <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route 123/Dolly Madison Boulevard</i></b>. Continue on Dolly Madison Boulevard for approx. 1.3 miles toward <span style="COLOR: red">McLean</span> and turn<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"> RIGHT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Elm Street</i></b> (this is shortly after crossing Old Dominion Drive) to: <span style="COLOR: #660000"><a href="https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=200153348770417974908.0004c355ae2c000c7a63c&msa=0&ll=38.935294,-77.178333&spn=0.006952,0.013937"><font color="#0000ff">6862 Elm Street, McLean, VA</font></a></span>. Park and look for wankers milling around.</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></p><p /><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">From I-495:</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "> Find your way to: <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">I-495: </b>Take <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">EXIT 46B</b> for <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route 123/Dolley Madison Boulevard</i></b> toward <span style="COLOR: red">McLean</span>. Continue on Dolly Madison Boulevard for approx. 2.3 miles toward <span style="COLOR: red">McLean</span> and turn<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"> RIGHT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Elm Street</i></b> (this is shortly after crossing Old Dominion Drive) to: <span style="COLOR: #660000"><a href="https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=200153348770417974908.0004c355ae2c000c7a63c&msa=0&ll=38.935294,-77.178333&spn=0.006952,0.013937"><font color="#0000ff">6862 Elm Street, McLean, VA</font></a></span>. Park and look for wankers milling around.</span></p><p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">From George Washington Memorial Parkway:</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "> Find your way to: <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">George Washington Memorial Parkway</b> toward Cabin John Bridge<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">: </b>Take the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">EXIT </b>for <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Route 123/Dolley Madison Boulevard</i></b> toward <span style="COLOR: red">McLean</span>. Continue on Dolly Madison Boulevard for approx. 2.5 miles toward <span style="COLOR: red">McLean</span> and turn<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"> LEFT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Churchhill Road</i></b> then take the <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">1<sup>st</sup> RIGHT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Fleetwood Road</i></b>, and then a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">LEFT</b> onto <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><i style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal">Elm Street</i></b> to: <span style="COLOR: #660000"><a href="https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=200153348770417974908.0004c355ae2c000c7a63c&msa=0&ll=38.935294,-77.178333&spn=0.006952,0.013937"><font color="#0000ff">6862 Elm Street, McLean, VA</font></a></span>. Park and look for wankers milling around.</span></p>', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Where else… “The Pub”!! (next to the Peking Restaurant… same owner. Drink in “The Pub” or order food in the smoke-free Peking Restaurant.</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">“The Pub” ~ Peking Restaurant<br /></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><a href="https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=200153348770417974908.0004c355ae2c000c7a63c&msa=0&ll=38.935294,-77.178333&spn=0.006952,0.013937"><font color="#0000ff">6827 Redmond Drive</font></a><br /></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">McLean, VA<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>22102<br /></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">(703) 448-0928</span></p>', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Final Disclaimer:</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "> Bring dry clothes and shoes, bug spray, sunscreen (NOT!!), condoms (as always… be safe!!), your grandmother’s underwear (why… we don’t know. Hummm… or is it… you never know?), and your appetite for some fine beers from all over the world!! And… finally… should we remind you… shiggy-socks and/or PI Block.</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "></span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Oh… and please don’t forget those beautiful, young Russian female virgins!!</span></p>', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><a href="https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=200153348770417974908.0004c355ae2c000c7a63c&msa=0&ll=38.935294,-77.178333&spn=0.006952,0.013937"><font color="#0000ff">Trail#531</font></a></span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Back parking lot behind Long &amp; Foster: <a href="https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=200153348770417974908.0004c355ae2c000c7a63c&msa=0&ll=38.935294,-77.178333&spn=0.006952,0.013937"><font color="#0000ff">6862 Elm Street, McLean, VA</font></a></span> </p>', ''),
(531, '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: \'Georgia\',\'serif\'; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">I was working on my crossword puzzles the other day in my favorite library (you know… the one with the ‘white’ chair, BIG HOLE?) anyway… Puzzle 17 ~ 51 Across ~ “(blank) and hounds (outdoor game).<br /><br />Any guesses?<br /><br />That’s RIGHT!!<br /><br />So… it obviously <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">MUST</b> be a <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">SIGN!!</b> The So Happy It’s Tuesday Hash House Harriers 530<sup>th</sup> Trail!! AND… the 5<sup>th</sup> Leg of the Tour d’Hash!!</span></span></p>', '<p />', '<span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span><strong>On-On-On: </strong><a href="http://www.glorydaysgrill.com/"><font color="#0000ff">Glory Days Bar &amp; Grill</font></a> (Pan Am Shopping Center)</span></p><p /><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=en&cp=35&gs_id=2&xhr=t&q=3059+nutley+street+fairfax+va+22031&gs_upl=&bav=on.2,or.r_gc.r_pw.,cf.osb&biw=1920&bih=899&wrapid=tljp132231855548600&um=1&ie=UTF-8&hq=&hnear=0x89b64b8a859f8f5f:0xca99d4ef2e03e6e4,3059+Nutley+St,+Fairfax,+VA+22031&gl=us&ei=0_rQToTNIMje0QGsgo3pDw&sa=X&oi=geocode_result&ct=title&resnum=1&sqi=2&ved=0CBwQ8gEwAA"><font color="#0000ff">3059 Nutley Street</font></a><br />Fairfax, VA 22031<br />703.201.0900</span></p><p /><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Directions to the OnOnOn: WALK to the FRONT parking lot!!</span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Specials: TBA</span></p></span>', '', '<span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?hl=en&cp=33&gs_id=8&xhr=t&q=3059+nutley+street+fairfax+va+22031&gs_upl=&bav=on.2,or.r_gc.r_pw.,cf.osb&biw=1920&bih=899&wrapid=tljp132231641029000&um