(534, '<ul type="disc"><li style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1" class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-ansi-language: EN" lang="EN"><a title="1839" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1839"><font color="#0000ff">1839</font></a> – <a title="Adolphus Busch" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adolphus_Busch"><font color="#0000ff">Adolphus Busch</font></a>, German-born brewer (d. 1913)<p /></span></li></ul><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">What better than to<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>celebrate the birth of<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Colonel Adolphus Busch</b> {10 July 1839 – 10 October 1913} who was the German-born co-founder of </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Anheuser-Busch</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: "> with his father-in-law, <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">Eberhard Anheuser</b>. His grea-great-gandson, <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">August Busch IV</b> is now on the board of </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">Anheuser-Busch InBev</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">.</span></p><p />', '<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: 45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt" class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="COLOR: black">METRO:</span></b><span style="COLOR: black"> Sorry… not </span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">METRO ACCESSIBLE</span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: ">, however, check the bus schedules (7A or DASH BUS 2) to get you there… WINK?</span><span style="COLOR: black"></span></p><p /><p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: 45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 50