(548, 'In honor of Leif Erickson Day, we will be rediscovering trail in this area that may have been previously used.<div>Wait, did I get that backwards?<br /><div><br /></div></div>', 'Get to Herndon Parkway<div>Turn onto Queens Row St (going East)</div><div>Make your first right</div><div>Park in the pool parking lot</div>', 'Carpool<div><div>208 Elden Street, Herndon, VA</div><div>(571) 203-7995</div></div>', 'Bring a dry bag, PI block, tick block, and several lights. Yes, several, because you know everyone else will forget theirs, and try to borrow yours', 'Runnymede Park, Herndon VA<div>38.976870, -77.369003</div>', ''),
(551, '<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; ">It\'s the night before all hollows eve and we just want to dring a round or two at some of our favorite watering holes.</span><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">What to expect: It is our 550 so there might be a toe tag to commisorate the evening, a warm and wonderful shot or two and some local eye candy.</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">What not to expect: a runners trail, this is a pub CRAWL!</div>', '<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; ">From  Toll road take Herndon/Chantilly exit onto Elden Street (Worldgate exit).  Take a right on Elden St and stay on it  pass the shops and stores.  When it turns to a two lane road look for Center Street on your left.  Take left then take a right into the rear parking lot.  Look for spooky wankers.</span><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">Fairfax County Parkway get off onto Elden Street and go a few miles until you hit the center of town; look for old looking building on your right and a funeral home on your left.  take a right onto Lynn St then immediate lefft into the parking lot.  Drive to rear and find us</div>', '&nbsp;', '<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">No hash cash for this one, just come on out, wear a costume and bring an ID and cash for at least 4 bars.</span>', '<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">Parking lot behind Ice House Resturant across from Art Explosion in Herndon - </span><span dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">754 Elden Street #102, Herndon, VA</span>', '');
