(549, '<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); ">Alaska Day is a legal holiday in the U.S. State of Alaska, which… obviously is observed on the 18</span><sup style="font-family: Georgia; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); ">th</sup><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); ">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); ">of October in celebration of  The United States’ purchase of said state from Russia for $7.2 million (I’m sure they didn’t see THAT coming) in 1867!!</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><br /></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">Alaska Day is observed statewide, and is a paid holiday for State of Alaska employees (see… now you’re wishing that you live in Alaska so you can get that extra paid holiday… aren’t ya?)</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><br /></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">On the NEXT “October 18<sup>th</sup> (anyone got a calendar?)… we’re going to have “Puerto Rico” day hash… in honor of The United States taking possession of Puerto Rico in 1898!!</span></font></p>', '<b style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; "><font face="Georgia">From Sterling/Herndon/Reston:</font></b><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">Take <b>Route 28/Sully Road</b> to the <b>EXIT</b> for <u><u><b><i>Waxpool Road</i></b><u><u>. Continue on <u><u>Waxpool Road<u><u> for approx. 1½ miles and turn <b>LEFT</b> onto <b><i>Loudoun County Parkway</i></b>. Continue on <u><u>Loudoun County Parkway<u><u> for another 1½ miles and turn<b>RIGHT</b> onto <u><u><b><i>Shellhorn Road</i></b><u><u>. Turn <b>LEFT</b> onto <u><u><b><i>Metro Center Drive</i></b><u><u> (this is just after <u><u>Devin Shafron Drive<u><u>) and continue toward the end and turn <b>RIGHT</b> into the empty parking lot… look for wankers milling around.<u><u /></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><u><u><u><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; "><u> <u /></u></span></font></u></u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><u><u><u><b><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">From I-495:</span></font></b><font face="Georgia"> Find your way to: <b>I-495: </b>Towards <font color="red">Tysons Corner</font> and take the <b>EXIT</b> for <u><u><b><i>VA-267 Dulles Toll Road</i></b><u><u>. After going through the main tolls (and paying a $1.50 pre-hash contribution)… you have two options:<u><u /></u></u></u></u></u></font></u></u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><u><u><u><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; "><u> <u /></u></span></font></u></u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><u><u><u><b><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">Option A: (the less expensive, but plan ahead due to traffic)<u><u /></u></span></font></b></u></u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><u><u><u><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">Continue on <u><u>VA-267 Dulles Toll Road<u><u> to the last exit before the Greenway and take <b>EXIT 9B</b> for <b>Route 28/Sully Road, North</b> (after another $ .75 pre-hash contribution) towards <u><u><font color="red">Sterling</font><u><u> and follow the directions above.<u><u /></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></span></font></u></u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><u><u><u><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; "><u> <u /></u></span></font></u></u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><u><u><u><b><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">Option B: (the more expensive, but you will get there 2 or 3 hours before hash time… give or take 2 or 3 hours)<u><u /></u></span></font></b></u></u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><u><u><u><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">Continue on <u><u>VA-267 Dulles Toll Road<u><u> through the tolls at the Greenway (and pay a $4.75 (or $5.55 for the CONGESTION MANAGEMENT TOLL) pre-hash contribution). Take <b>EXIT 7</b> for <u><u><b>Loudoun County Parkway</b><u><u>. Turn<b>RIGHT</b> onto <u><u><b><i>Loudoun County Parkway</i></b><u><u> and then <b>LEFT</b> onto <u><u><b><i>Shellhorn Road</i></b><u><u>. Turn <b>LEFT</b> onto <u><u><b><i>Metro Center Drive</i></b><u><u> (this is just after <u><u>Devin Shafron Drive<u><u>) and continue toward the end and turn <b>RIGHT</b> into the empty parking lot… look for wankers milling around.</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></span></font></u></u></u></p><u><u><u>&nbsp;</u></u></u>', '<b style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">“<a href="http://www.redrobin.com/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=local&utm_content=583&utm_campaign=localmaps" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); ">Red Robin</a> Gourmet Burgers”</span></font></b><font face="Georgia" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">: <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?daddr=43530+Yukon+Drive+Ashburn%2C+VA+20147" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); ">43530 Yukon Drive</a>, Ashburn</font><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><font color="black" face="Georgia">, VA ~ </font></span><font face="Georgia" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><a href="tel:703.723.6005" value="+17037236005" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); ">703.723.6005</a></font>', '<b style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; "><font size="3" face="Georgia"><span style="font-size: 12pt; ">DON’T FORGET FLASHLIGHTS!!</span></font></b><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-famil