(552, '&nbsp;', '<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">From toll road - take the exit for Herndon/Chantilly and head onto Chantilly Road.  Go about 2 miles then turn right onto Sunrise Valley Road.  Take a right at the second drive into the parkinglot, got to the rear and look around.</span><div><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><br /></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">From Fairfax Co. Parkway - turn onto Sunrise Valley road towards Herdon (going pass the metro parking deck).  Continue on Sunrise Valley for 2-3 miles until you cross Chantilly road.  Cross Chantilly, go pass the park entrance and turn right into 13450.  Goto the rear and look for wankers.</span></div>', '<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">Ned Divines</span>', '<div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">Trail: A to Z but most likely A to B.  Bring dry bag and warm cloths.</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">It\'s getting cold and dark so prepare accordingly and remember to vote!</div>', '<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); ">Rear parking lot behind 13450 Sunrise Valley Drive office building</span>', ''),
(553, 'Did you know that the Czech Republic is surrounded mostly by mountains? No, of course this won\'t have any bearing on the trail we\'re about to run...', '<span style="font-size: 16px;">METRO:</span><br style="font-size: 16px;" /><span style="font-size: 16px;">Silver Line to the Whiele Ave Metro Station...you may have to wait for a few months for the train</span><div><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br /></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">FROM 286 (formerly 7100)</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">Turn onto Sunset Hill Rd</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">   this is a left if going South, a right if going North</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">Go over Whiele Ave</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">Make your next left onto Michael Faraday</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">Veer right, and find wankers in the back of the huge lot</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br /></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">FROM 267 (Dulles Toll Road)</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">Take the Whiele exit</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">Turn right onto Sunset Hills Rd</span></div><div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">Make your next left onto Michael Faraday</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 16px;">Veer right, and find wankers in the back of the huge lot</span></div></div>', '<span style="font-size: 12pt;">Champs Americana: 11694 Plaza America Drive, Reston, VA  20190</span><br />DRIVING: (from START)<br /><p style="background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-color: white; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat repeat;">EXIT Michael Faraday Court and turn RIGHT onto Sunset Hills Road ~<br />continue for 1.0 mile and turn RIGHT onto Plaza America Drive</p><div><br /></div>', 'A to A? A to Z? Who knows! It\'s cold, it\'s dark, and somehow the PI is still out there. Dress warmly, bring a few lights, bring