(583, 'It\'s national hugs day, so who better to lead you around than Parent\'s and Herpicles. But since these two bastards aren\'t allowed to do trail by themselves anymore, Taster\'s has the unpleasant doody of keeping them in check. Good luck!', 'From 28 or 66 - take exit for 50 and head towards the Greenbrier Shopping Center.  From 66 go to the 2nd light beyond the shopping center and take a left  onto Stringfellow &amp; from 28 take a right onto Stringfellow just before the shopping center. Follow Stringfellow for about 2-3 miles and look for park \'n ride just before the 66 overpass.  Look for wankers in the rear of the lot.', '<div>Red Rocks Cafe &amp; Tequila Bar</div><div>13850 Braddock Rd</div><div>Centreville, VA 20121</div>', '&nbsp;', '<div>Park and Ride commuter lot on Stringfellow Road in Chantilly, VA</div><div><br /></div>', ''),
(581, 'Get out your red &amp; white striped shirt, socks, and cap and help find Waldo\'s shirt. There will be a hunt for his stripes in and around Reston Park Center. Look high, look low, and follow the clues. There will be beer, maybe some Waldo shots, and definitely a trail to remember!', '<div>Start: Parking Lot for W&amp;OD Trail (adjacent to 7-11 corner of Sunset Hills &amp; Old Reston Avenue)</div><div>Address: 11714 Sunset Hills, Reston, VA  20190</div>', '<div>Champps Americana Sports Bar (corner of Sunset Hills &amp; Plaza America) -- across the street from the start.</div><div>Address:11694 Plaza America, Reston, VA 20190</div>', 'There will be NO Czech marks, so follow the occasional flour, a few arrows, some signs with red &amp; white stripes.', 'Parking Lot for W&amp;OD Trail (adjacent to 7-11 corner of Sunset Hills &amp; Old Reston Avenue)<div>11714 Sunset Hills, Reston, VA  20190</div>', ''),
(586, 'It\'s the 4th of July, and you know what that means? Something about setting off fireworks to scare away terrorists.<div>Wear red white and blue,  4th inspired trail with multiple american beer checks and shot checks</div>', 'The hares declined to give us any, so I\'d vote for a healthy does of google and gpses', 'HOOTERS!!!', 'Some heavy shiggy, so bring tick, lice, PI, and hobo repellent', 'Cub Run RECentermore<div>&#8206;4630 Stonecroft Boulevard</div><div>Chantilly, VA 20151</div><div>in the front parking lot.</div>', ''),
(582, 'After many weeks of begging and pleading, Vaginger finally agreed to do another trail for us. Now it\'s our turn to beg and plead with her to stop laying trail, and just let us drink already. Prepare to s*ck it up, and get f*cked', 'See above. Metro is A, B is start', '<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \'times new roman\', \'new york\', times, serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Velocity 5 in Vienna at the cornerish of Gallows and 29</span>', '<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \'times new roman\', \'new york\', times, serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">People they may need a second pair of shoes and bug spry other wise should be a good trail</span>', '<span style="font-family: \'times new roman\', \'new york\', times, serif; font-size: 16px;">8221 Wolftrap Rd</span><div><span style="font-family: \'times new roman\', \'new york\', times, serif; font-size: 16px;">Vienna, VA 22182</span><div><br /></div><div><a href="http://binged.it/15k4NOg">http://binged.it/15k4NOg\r\n</a></div></div>', '');
