(589, '<div>Okay…</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>So the title needs work!!</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>ALL of our trails have some kind of “Title”… it’s just something that distinquishes is from the rest. So… make up one of your own or leave it to Parent’s Weekend and/or The Udder Ho to be somewhat inventive.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>I, And How’s Her Bush, however… like to make up my own. And… if I don’t immediately come up with some cute title… I do the next best thing… I “Google” it!!</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Low and behold… you’ll find on this day, in history of course, the first Miss America pageant winner to have to give up her crown for what you ask? Nude photos purchased by Penthouse!!</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Venessa Williams was the first African-American woman to be crowned Miss America and subsequently made her career in acting. My favorite movie of hers was “Dance With Me”!!</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>So… grab your tiaras and come on out to the hash!!</div>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>METRO:</b> Sorry… not <b><span style="font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\', serif;">METRO ACCESSIBLE</span></b><span style="font-family: \'Bookman Old Style\', serif;"> at this time, however, it is 92% complete!! Hope they don’t run out of money to finish it!!</span><u><u /></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><u><u><u><u> <u /></u></u></u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><u><u><u><b>DRIVING:</b><u><u /></u></u></u></u></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><u><u><u><b>From the WEST: