(602, 'We just had our 599 trail last week, so it must be time for our 600th trail.<div>But wait, someone must have been a little drunk during the bookkeeping.</div><div>We\'re somehow at the 601st trail, so just shut up and enjoy the shiggy</div>', 'Cumming Soon', '<div>Champps Americana</div><div>Fair Oaks Mall</div><div>Fair Oaks, VA 22033</div>\r\n<div></div><div><a href=\'https://www.google.com/maps/ms?msid=208291817849788313232.0004e84fb045a17873bbb&msa=0&ll=38.86494,-77.363459&spn=0.007627,0.016512\'>I\'m the map</a></div>', 'It\'s dark before even the hares leave, so make sure to bring a light. Rivers and Creeks abound in this area, so make sure to bring a dry change of socks', 'The back lot of the Fairfax Towne Center<div>12210 Fairfax Towne Center</div><div>Fairfax, VA 22033</div><div></div><div><a href=\'https://www.google.com/maps/ms?msid=208291817849788313232.0004e84fb045a17873bbb&msa=0&ll=38.86494,-77.363459&spn=0.007627,0.016512\'>I\'m the map</a></div>', ''),
(601, '<div>Ten years ago, in a county far, far away 5 drunken fools (with the help of two supportive but equally drunken fools) pulled together a Kennel to fill the weekly emptiness known as Tuesday. &nbsp;This gathering would come to be known as the <i>So Happy It\'s Tuesday Hash House Harriers</i> and lay claim to trails filled with non urban shiggy and overly exuberant support of the many brands of Phillip Morris cigarettes.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Ten years later, the cigarette smoke has cleared and the SH*T, still smelling a little rank, continues it\'s mission by providing wankers with something on Tuesday to take the pain of the work-week away.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>On Sunday September 29th the SH*T will celebrate 10 years with it AGM. &nbsp;There will be beer, there will be trails and there will be more details to follow.</div><div><br></div><div><b>Please note a special start time of 12:00</b></div>', 'Cumming Soon!', 'Lost Rhino Brewing Company...Duh!<div>21730 Red Rum Drive, Suite 142, Ashburn, VA 20147</div>', '<div>SH*T MM has elected to share with you fine folks some additional</div><div>details regarding the AGM, which will be held this Sunday</div><div>September 29th in Ashburn, VA. There will be an excellent walker</div><div>and runner trail followed by food and beverages at the local Lost</div><div>Rhino brewery. The cost to you - $25.</div>', '21690 Red Rum Drive (behind Action Martial Arts)', ''),
