(605, 'It\'s just after Halloween, but don\'t let that stop you from dressing up.<div>Rebel against the establishment saying Halloween only lasts for 1 day English Style with your best Guy Fawkes mask.</div><div>Prizes will be awarded of course, but don\'t expect anything beyond an extra down down</div>', 'Sorry, none provided this week, so use the <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/ms?msid=204705530803267861617.0004ea38253fa9e23ef87&amp;msa=0&amp;ll=38.870838,-77.46284&amp;spn=0.00999,0.021136">map</a>', '<div><div>Blue Water Grille&nbsp;</div><div>5127 Westfields Blvd, Centreville, VA â€Ž</div></div>', 'It\'s dark early, so bring make sure you come out with those lights! Also, we have some new hab, so bring some extra cash or a checkbook!', 'Back lot of the Justice Federal Credit Union in Chantilly<div>5175 Parkstone Dr. Chantilly</div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://www.google.com/maps/ms?msid=204705530803267861617.0004ea38253fa9e23ef87&amp;msa=0&amp;ll=38.870838,-77.46284&amp;spn=0.00999,0.021136">I\'m the Map</a></div>', ''),
(600, 'Celebrating 40 years (or close enough).&nbsp;Theme? &nbsp;We don\'t need no stinkin\' theme!<div>Cum dressed as your favorite Blazing Saddles character... &nbsp;or not.<div><br></div></div>', 'Cumming Soon!', '<div>TBD</div>\r\n<div><a href=\'https://www.google.com/maps/ms?msid=208291817849788313232.0004e7ea67597d549416f&msa=0&ll=38.798524,-77.299622&spn=0.001909,0.004128\'>I\'m The Map!</a></div>', '<p style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0.3em; line-height: 18px; padding: 0px;">Now, I suppose you\'re all wondering just what in the heck you\'re doing out here in the middle of a prairie in the middle of nowhere in the middle of the night.</p><p style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0.3em; line-height: 18px; padding: 0px;">You bet your ass!</p><p style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0.3em; line-height: 18px; padding: 0px;"><br></p><p style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 0.3em; line-height: 18px; padding: 0px;">Trail is A to B, so bring a dry bag. Also, it\'ll be dark before we even leave, so make sure to bring a light!</p>', '<div>The back lot at Target in Burke. &nbsp;</div><div>10301 New Guinea Road</div><div>Fairfax, VA 22032</div><div><br></div>\r\n<div><a href=\'https://www.google.com/maps/ms?msid=208291817849788313232.0004e7ea67597d549416f&msa=0&ll=38.798524,-77.299622&spn=0.001909,0.004128\'>I\'m The Map!</a></div>', ''),
