(628, '<div>On April 15th, we have a unholy combination of events occuring! A</div><div>Blood Moon Lunar Eclipse, Passover and most forboding of all..... TAX</div><div>DAY! Come join us as we try to do what the IRS has been doing for</div><div>years, squeezing blood out of a rock (or hasher&apos;s legs in our case!)</div><div>and then drown your sorrows with fellow wankers over having to shell</div><div>out your hard earned money to the Tax Man. We promise shiggy (wet and</div><div>dry) and beverage checks (hard and soft), what more could you ask</div><div>for?! We plan to offer up our Virgin Hare Just Austin to the Angel of</div><div>Death in true passover fashion!</div>', '<b>From the (South) East:</b><div>Get to 66.</div><div>Take it West</div><div>If you are HOV 2+ (or are running late and it is after 7pm)</div><blockquote style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div style="margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Take the Stringfellow Exit (the left exit right after exit 55).</div></blockquote><blockquote style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div style="margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Go Left at the light on Stringfellow</div></blockquote><blockquote style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div style="margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Turn Left onto Autumn Willow Dr</div><div style="margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Make your first Left into the Soccer Fields</div></blockquote>If you are&nbsp;<b>NOT</b>&nbsp;HOV compliant and on time<div><blockquote style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div style="margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Take exit 55, and head South on Fairfax County Park