(630, '<b>Pre-lewb:</b><div>Jimmy&apos;s Old Town Tavern</div><div>697 Spring Street, Herndon, VA</div>', '<div><b>From the North/West</b>: (Ashburn/Sterling/Herndon/Reston): &nbsp;</div><div>Really ... OK, Go southeast on VA-7 E and take the Virginia 28 S ramp to Dulles Airport/Centreville. &nbsp;After about 4.5 miles exit onto VA-606 E/Old Ox Rd toward Herndon and continue to follow VA-606 E for about &nbsp;2.3 miles. &nbsp;Turn left onto Elden St for about &nbsp;0.4 mile then turn left onto Center St. &nbsp;Your destination will be on the right, just look for Wankers. &nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><b>From the BELTWAY</b>:</div><div>Take I-495 to exit 47A/Virginia 7/Leesburg Pike/Falls Church &nbsp;merge onto VA-7 W/Leesburg Pike. &nbsp;After about 7.2 miles turn left onto Baron Cameron Ave for about 3 miles. &nbsp;The road will change to Elden St, continue for another 1.3 miles before turning right onto Center St. &nbsp;Your destination will be on the right, just look for Wankers. &nbsp;&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><b>From the South</b>:</div><div>Take I-95 North to exit 160B and merge onto VA-123. &nbsp;After about 10 miles take ramp right onto VA 286 North Fairfax County Parkway. &nbsp;Go about 15 miles and exit onto VA-606W Elden St for about 1.3 miles before turning right onto Center St. &nbsp;Your destination will be on the right, just look for Wankers. &nbsp;&nbsp;</div>', '<div>O&apos;Sullivan&apos;s Irish Pub</div><div><div>754 Elden Street #102, Herndon, VA</div><div><span id="gc-number-0" class="gc-cs-link" title="Call with Google Voice">(703) 464-0522</span></div></div>', '<div><b>BRING A FLASHLIGHT!!</b> You know... just in case!! And need I remind you of the standard disclaimers?</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><b>Dog Friendly Factor:</b> Tough Dogs Should Be Fine...</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><b>Stroller Friendly Factor:</b> Not A Chance!!</div><div><br></div><div><b>Final Disclaimer: </b>Bring dry clothes and shoes, bug spray, sunscreen (NOT!!)