(631, 'I&apos;m sorry, what&apos;s that? You don&apos;t regularly celebrate Seis de Mayo. What kind of dirty hippy are you?<div>Here at shit we have a hard enough time getting to work (ok...the bar...) on time. So of course we can&apos;t keep track of our holidays.</div><div>We celebrate how and when we want to.&nbsp;</div><div>So come out in your most festive Mexican-American battle garb (that&apos;s right, it&apos;s not Mexican Independence day, we&apos;re celebrating a victory in a battle. We&apos;re lazy, not ignorant here), and be prepared for a very special trail</div>', 'Cumming Soon', '<div>Coyote Grille</div><div>10266 Main St</div><div>Fairfax, VA 22030</div>', '<div><b>BRING A FLASHLIGHT!!</b>&nbsp;You know... just in case!! And need I remind you of the standard disclaimers?</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><b>Dog Friendly Factor:</b>&nbsp;Tough Dogs Should Be Fine...</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><b>Stroller Friendly Factor:</b>&nbsp;Not A Chance!!</div><div><br></div><div><b>Final Disclaimer:&nbsp;</b>Bring dry clothes and shoes, bug spray, sunscreen (NOT!!), condoms (as always... be safe!!), your grandmother&apos;s underwear (why... we don&apos;t know. Hummm... or is it... you never know?), and your appetite for some fine beers from all over the world!! And... finally... should we remind you... shiggy-socks and/or PI Block.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Oh... and please don&apos;t forget those beautiful, young female virgins!!</div>', '3927 Old Lee Hwy, Fairfax, VA', 'https://www.google.com/maps/ms?msid=208291817849788313232.0004f86a464672cf499d7&msa=0&ll=38.846593,-77.300599&spn=0.007194,0.016512'),
