(643, 'It&apos;s only taken an extra year, but trail is metro accessible.<div><br></div><div>Wait...what...we&apos;re metro accessible?!?</div>', '<div>Driving directions: From Dulles Toll Rd, exit at Wiehle Ave, going north on Wiehle. Proceed a few blocks and turn left onto Sunset Hills Rd. Make the first right, through the commuter lot on Isaac Newton Sq. West. Cross the W&amp;OD trail and make the first left into the parking lot.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Metro directions: Take the Silver Line to the Wiehle Station. Exit the station on the north side. Follow Metro Center Dr north 1 block and cross Sunset Hills Rd. The street changes names to Isaac Newton Sq. West. Cross the W&amp;OD trail and make the first left into the parking lot.&nbsp;</div>', '', '<div>The trail is A - B. A bag vehicle will be provided. The trail is dog friendly, but not stroller friendly.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div>', '<div>1984 Fairway Executive Center - Isaac Newton Sq. West.</div>', 'https://www.google.com/maps/ms?msid=208291817849788313232.0004ff55aed6c74772c03&msa=0&ll=38.952588,-77.339839&spn=0.001954,0.003954'),
