(647, '<div>Seriously... National "Bad" Dog Day?</div><div>That&apos;s right... National "Bad" Dog Day was founded in 2004 to show appreciation for dogs and their connection to humans (actually... MOST dogs THINK they&apos;re human... right "Bad Dog"?).</div><div>So... come on out this Tuesday and bring your little furry friend... and see what the hares have in store for you. If you don&apos;t have a furry friend... I&apos;m sure we can find one for you to pet (right "Bad Dog"?)!!</div><div>Ironically... this day comes at an opportune time... Isn&apos;t it... "Bad Dog&apos;s" birthday as well?</div><div>By the way... let me remind everyone that our current Sunset is now coming before 08:00pm. Hummm... what does that mean really? BRING A FLASHLIGHT!!</div><div>Besides... you know what kind of trail "Bad Dog" likes... tunnels, caves, drain pipes, creeks, swamps, and maybe some mountain climbing!!</div><div>Now... onto more important information!!</div>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><b><span style="color: black;">METRO:</span></b><span style="color: black;">&nbsp;</span><b><span style="font-family: &apos;Bookman Old Style&apos;, serif; color: black;">METRO? Did someone say, METRO?</span></b><span style="font-family: &apos;Bookman Old Style&apos;, serif; color: black;">&nbsp;Sorry... not this week!!<u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="font-family: &apos;Times New Roman&apos;, serif; color: black;"><u></u>&nbsp;<u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><b><span style="color: black;">DRIVING: (From the WEST: Sterling/Herndon/Reston):<u></u><u></u></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-fa