(670, '<div>How many many people does it take to 69.... 6! Cum to this weeks 669th Penis and Vagina trail which promises to be wet, muddy, and cold just like every 69 should be. Wait, thats not how you 69?&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Bring a headlamp, a change of clothes (seriously, otherwise Flower will hose you down before she lets you into her house. You WILL get wet and muddy), and something to share at the POTLUCK. Pre-lub, Start, and On-After are at Flowers - 7553 Great Swan Ct. Alexandria, VA 22306. Visitor parking is in middle, as well as on Cyrene Blvd (main road).</div>', '<div>Type in address to google on your phone, computer, or GPS or try and follow what Mr. Google gave us below. See you there ;-)</div><div><br></div><div><b>From The North:</b></div><div>Go southeast on George Washington Memorial Pkwy, take a slight right toward Slaters Lane (signs for Slaters Lane/Bashford Lane/W Abingdon) for 0.2 miles and take the 1st right onto Slaters Lane. Take the ramp onto U.S. 1 S/N Henry Street and follow U.S. 1 S about 5 miles. Turn right onto Fordson Road and after 92 feet turn left to stay on Fordson Road . After 0.6 miles turn right onto Cyrene Blvd and take the 3rd right onto Great Swan Court. Destination will be on the left, look for wankers and park.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><b>From The West:</b></div><div>Go east on I-66 E and take exit 64A to merge onto I-495 S toward Richmond for about 12.5 miles and keep right at the fork to continue on I-495 E/I-95 N, follow signs for Telegraph Road/Virginia 241/Huntington/Alexandria. After 0.6 miles take exit 176A for Virginia 241 S/Telegraph Road/Virginia 611 S onto VA-241 S for 1.3 miles and turn right onto U.S. 1 S for 1.5 miles. Turn right onto Fordson Road and after 92 feet turn left to stay on Fordson Road . After 0.6 miles turn right onto Cyrene Blvd and take the 3rd right onto Great Swan Court. Destination will be on the left, look for wankers and park.</div><div><br></div><div><b>From The South:</b></div><div>Go North on I-95 and take exit 161 to merge onto U.S. 1 N toward Ft Belvoir/Mt Vernon for about 11.5 miles. Turn left onto Lockheed Blvd&nbsp;</div><div>for 476 feet and then turn left onto Fordson Road for about .5 mile and take the 3rd right onto Cyrene Blvd for 0.2 miles and take the 3rd right onto Great Swan Court. Destination will be on the left, look for wankers and park.</div>', 'POTLUCK at Casa De Flower<div>7553 Great Swan Ct</div><div>Alexandria, VA 22306</div>', '<div>BRING A FLASHLIGHT!! And make sure it has working batteries!! And need I remind you of the standard disclaimers?</div><div><br></div><div><b>Dog Friendly Factor</b>: Dogs OK on trail and at Circle, but will be banished to the back yard durring On-After due to number of cats occupying the crazy cat lady&apos;s abode.</div><div><br></div><div><b>Stroller Friendly Factor</b>: Tough Strollers Only...</div><div><br></div><div><b>Final Disclaimer</b>: Bring dry clothes and shoes, bug spray, sunscreen (NOT!!), condoms (as always... be safe!!), your grandmother&apos;s underwear (why... we don&apos;t know. Hummm... or is it... you never know?), and your appetite for some fine beers from all over the world!! And... finally... should we remind you... shiggy-socks and/or PI Block.</div><div><br></div><div>Oh... and please don&apos;t forget those beautiful, young female virgins!!</div><div><br></div><div>QUESTIONS: Contact And How&apos;s Her Bush: AndHowsHerBush@yahoo.com</div><div><br></div><div>ON ON Penis and Vagina ON ON</div>', 'Casa De Flower<div>7553 Great Swan Ct</div><div>Alexandria, VA 22306</div>', '');
