(673, '<div>SHIFT to be official.</div><div><br></div><div>It&apos;s time to consider giving up the sinful and glutenous actions that have made 2015 what is is (so far). &nbsp;but first you need to have a last hurrah and celebrate with reckless abandon; this is where SH*T happens!</div><div><br></div><div>Back to Arlington to make those with the inability to travel to the badlands experience a touch of Happiness.</div>', '<div><b>Driving</b>: take 66E toward Arlington and exit onto Fairfax Drive. &nbsp;Go about 7 blocks or so then take a left onto N Quincy and follow pass the High school. &nbsp;After the HS take a left onto 15th &nbsp;St N and deck will be on your left.</div><div><br></div><div><b>Metro</b>: why yes there is!! &nbsp;Carefully exit at Ballston and head towards IHOP (do not stop in or you may never leave). &nbsp;Cross over onto N Stafford and head towards the HS. &nbsp;Pass teh HS and go upstairs to the far corner of the upper deck.</div><div><br></div>', 'A - Town @ Fairfax Drive and Randolf St.', '<div>Trail is A to A, should be dog friendly but not at the OnOnOn.</div><div><div>BRING A FLASHLIGHT!! You know... just in case!! And need I remind you of the standard disclaimers?</div><div>Bring your Feathered Masks, Beads, best Mardi Gras clothes, and virgins for Fat Tuesday sacrifices.</div></div>', 'Ballston parking deck about route 66 - upper decker cause that&apos;s how we do it<br>4000 15th Street North, Arlington, VA 22207', ''),
(674, '<div>Abe Vigoda is Not Dead (Yet)</div><div>Come to the hash and drink to the health of Abe Vigoda on his 94th birthday! Contrary to the reports made in &apos;82 and &apos;87, Abe is not dead yet. Let&apos;s celebrate that this perpetual old guy is still here, 34 years since Michael Corleone had Sally Tessio whacked. Let&apos;s not wait to late to hoist one to a man who&apos;s outlasted prohibition, the Soviet Union, and Segregation in American schools!</div>', '<div>From the Capital Beltway (495)</div><div>Take exit 45 to Route 267 West (Dulles Toll Road), follow signs to local exits, pay a $2.50 toll, and exit at the Wolf Trap ramp. The Filene Center will be on the right.</div><div><br></div><div>From Route 7 Westbound (toward Leesburg)</div><div>Turn left on Towlston Road, drive 1 mile, and the Filene Center will be on the left.</div><div><br></div><div>From Route 123 in Vienna</div><div>Take route 123 North towards Tysons Corner. Turn left onto Old Courthouse Road. Turn left to stay on Old Courthouse Road. Follow Old Courthouse Road for 2 miles and turn right onto Trap Road. At the stop sign, turn left to stay on Trap Road. Drive 1/2 mile and the Filene Center will be on the right.</div>', 'BJ&apos;s? Chicks n wings? That newish Irish bar? Other?', 'Dog friendly, not stroller friendly.', '<div>Wolf Trap National Park for the Performing Arts: West Parking Lot</div><div>1551 Trap Road | Vienna, Virginia 22182</div>', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/Wolf+Trap+National+Park+for+the+Performing+Arts/@38.9398622,-77.2639977,16z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0000000000000000:0x65bd388e6de9cd3f'),
(675, 'Because Doc Cock didn&apos;t provide any theme for us this week, I have taken it upon myself to call him out.<div>So, this week&apos;s trail is what it is. And while I hate that phrase, it seems appropriate.</div><div>All of that said, come out and enjoy what is sure to be a truly shitty trail this Tuesday.</div>', 'Google all the way.<div>https://www.google.com/maps/dir//38.975718,-77.335878/@38.975718,-77.335878,17z/data=!4m5!1m4!3m3!1s0x0:0x0!2zMzjCsDU4JzMyLjYiTiA3N8KwMjAnMDkuMiJX!3b1</div>', 'Kalypso&apos;s Sports Tavern<div>1617 Washington Plaza North</div><div>Reston, VA 20190</div>', '<div>Trail is A to A, should be dog friendly but not at the OnOnOn.</div><div>BRING A FLASHLIGHT!! You know... just in case!! And need I remind you of the standard disclaimers?</div>', '<div>Baron Cameron Park in the parking lot for the soccer fields. The GPS coordinates are approximately</div><div><br></div><div>38.975718, -77.335878</div>', 'https://www.google.com/maps/d/edit?mid=z8oA6gJ-rfLo.kAZEzzHdA6rw'),
