(698, '<font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">Well...</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">At least it (the caption) got your\nattention... didn&apos;t it!?!</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">START of this week&apos;s trail is in the far\nback parking lot of the "</font><a href="http://loudounstation.com/"><font color="#0000ff" face="Georgia" size="3">Loudoun Station</font></a><font size="3">"\ncomplex. "</font><a href="http://loudounstation.com/"><font color="#0000ff" face="Georgia" size="3">Loudoun Station</font></a><font size="3">" is a signature\n"downtown" community with an</font></span><font size="3"><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000"> exciting mix of shops,\nrestaurants, residences, and offices, along with a hotel and 11-screen movie\ntheater...a vibra