Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">RETAIL:</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p align="center" style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-outline-level: 6;"><b><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">ALL ABOARD FOR GREAT SHOPPING, DINING, FUN &amp; GAMES</font></span></b></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">Loudoun Station is one of the most dynamic destinations\nin the Washington region. Centrally located in the most affluent and fastest\ngrowing county in Virginia, Loudoun Station will feature 300,000 square feet of\nretail in a mixed use urban setting. Currently 60,000 square feet of retail has\nbeen delivered with 357 luxury apartments above.</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">Retail highlights include Title Boxing, Burger 21, Kumon\nLearning Center, fi DENTAL, InStyle Nails Spa, the Zone and Starplex Cinemas.\nStarplex Cinemas will have 11 theaters including an Intense Digital Experience\n(IDX) screen, scheduled to open April 2015. The iconic cinema building is\n115,000 square feet and also houses a 9,000 square foot restaurant space and\n50,000 square feet of office.</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">RESIDENTIAL: </font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p align="center" style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-outline-level: 6;"><b><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">LUXURIOUS LIVING IN THE HEART OF LOUDOUN</font></span></b></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">Loudoun County&apos;s most appealing new community now has\nhomes available, offering trend-setting style and an array of amenities. BLVD |\nLoudoun Station features 357 luxury apartments in three mid-rise towers, with\nstudio, one-bedroom, and two-bedroom plus den options available.</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">Loudoun Station&apos;s shops, services, restaurants, cafes,\nand entertainment venues are steps away, along with convenient ground-floor\nretail within the building. BLVD | Loudoun Station tenants will also enjoy:</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">OFFICE SPACE:</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p align="center" style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-outline-level: 6;"><b><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">PREMIER LOCATION, PRIME VISIBILITY</font></span></b></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">Planned for 1.3 million square feet of Class A office\nspace, Loudoun Station offers unbeatable advantages to businesses seeking a\nMetro location, prime visibility, and optimum convenience. The mixed use\ncommunity combines distinctive architecture and urban parks with easy access to\npublic transportation and numerous amenities.</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">This remarkable office environment provides opportunities\nfor high-profile visibility and signage along the well-traveled Dulles Greenway\nand within one of the nation&apos;s most prominent business communities. Corporate\nneighbors include Raytheon, Booz Allen Hamilton, Cisco Systems, AOL, Verizon,\nand Microsoft. Loudoun Station&apos;s tenant-friendly location features a central\ngreen and plazas that create an engaging day-night atmosphere within this\nlive-work-play setting. The development&apos;s many restaurants, shops, services,\nand hotel accommodations support a host of day-to-day business needs.</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">HOTEL:</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p align="center" style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-outline-level: 6;"><b><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">STAY A WHILE...AT LOUDOUN STATION</font></span></b></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">Loudoun Station&apos;s full-service hotel (flag to be\ndetermined) will offer 200+ guest rooms and extensive amenities to serve\nbusiness travelers, tourists, and families. With an ideal location close to\nmany shops and restaurants, these premier accommodations offer much more than\nin-room comfort and impeccable service. An expansive, fully equipped conference\ncenter will support a range of meeting needs.</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span lang="EN" style=&apos;font-family: "Helvetica","sans-serif"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: EN;&apos;><font color="#000000">Travel couldn&apos;t be simpler with Loudoun Station&apos;s\nstrategic location along the Dulles Greenway and Metro&apos;s Silver Line extension.\nReston, Tysons Corner, and Washington, D.C., will be a quick, one-seat Metro\nride away. Washington-Dulles International Airport is just seven miles away,\neasily accessible by car or Metro.</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">But... I digress... because... </font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">With that being said... this week&apos;s tra