(701, 'The next DC Full Moon Trail is hosted by So Happy It&apos;s Tuesday Hash House Harriers on Friday the 25th of Sept, 2015 at 7 P.M', '<div><b>From the Beltway:</b> Take I-66 &nbsp;West to Exit 55. Take VA 286(Fairfax County Parkway)North to Fair Lakes Parkway and turn Left</div><div>onto Fair Lakes Parkway. After about 3 stoplights make a Left onto Fair Lakes Blvd for 1/2 mile. Make a Left onto Stringfellow Road, and an immediate Right into the Park</div><div>&amp; Ride lot before going under I-66.</div>', '<div>SHIT H3 will be BBQ&apos;ing at Parents Weekend&apos;s house. &nbsp;BBQ style food will be provided, but feel free to bring Meat to grill, or a</div><div>side-dish to share</div>', 'NOTE: The cost is $10<div>This is an A to B trail - there is limited parking at B so will NOT be vehicle runs until after circle. A is about 4 blocks from B</div>', 'The Stringfellow Park &amp; Ride Lot<div>4920 Stringfellow Road</div><div>Fairfax, VA 22030</div>', ''),
(702, '<div>Hummm...</div><div><br></div><div>A "Great Falls" trail on Tuesday?</div><div><br></div><div>Who woudda thunk it!?!</div><div>Bad Dog is recruiting 24/7... last week in a discussion he had with a Great Falls Hasher, to be identified later, he finds out that this wanker bought a new place and hadn&apos;t yet sold the other (River Bend Road).</div><div><br></div><div>"And How&apos;s Her Bush" &nbsp;were planning their next trail in Great Falls (see where I&apos;m going here...) Wa&apos;la!!</div><div>A marrage made in heaven!!</div>', '<div>METRO: METRO? Did someone say, METRO? In Great Falls? PLEASE!!</div><div><br></div><div>DRIVING:&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>From the WEST Via Route 7: (Sterling/Herndon/Reston):</div><div><br></div><div>Take a LEFT onto Georgetown Pike towards McLean (if cumming from Reston take&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Baron Cameron Avenue across Route 7 which then turns into Springvale Road to&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Georgetown Pike... Turn RIGHT onto Georgetown Pike). Continue on Georgetown&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Pike through Great Falls toward Great Falls Park. Turn &nbsp;LEFT onto River Road and&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>continue for approx. 1.2 miles to: 509 River Bend Road, Great Falls VA &nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>22066".</div><div><br></div><div>Look for wankers milling around.</div><div><br></div><div>From the BELTWAY:&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Find your way to the Beltway and take the EXIT for the Georgetown Pike towards&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Great Falls. Continue on Georgetown Pike past the entrance for Great Falls Park and take&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>first RIGHT onto River Road and continue for approx. 1.2 miles to: 509 River Bend&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Road, Great Falls VA &nbsp;22066".</div><div><br></div><div>Look for wankers milling around.</div>', '<div>On-On-On: The Old Brogue Irish Pub: 760 Walker Road, Great Falls, VA &nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>22066 ~ <span id="gc-number-0" class="gc-cs-link" title="Call with Google Voice">703-759-3309</span></div><div><br></div><div>D&apos;ERECTIONS:&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>FROM "START":&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Take a RIGHT onto Georgetown Pike ~ Continue to the town of Great Falls ~ Continue&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>past Walker Road ~ Turn LEFT into the shopping center to: Buffalo Wild Wings:&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>21980 Colorado Drive, Dulles 28 Centre, Sterling, VA&nbsp;</div>', '<div>BRING A FLASHLIGHT!! You know... just in case!! And need I</div><div><br></div><div>remind you of the standard disclaimers?</div><div><br></div><div>Miscellaneous: Trail will be... A to A&apos;:</div><div><br></div><div>(translated... the OTHER end of the parking lot!!)</div><div><br></div><div>Dog Friendly Factor: Tough Dogs Only...</div><div><br></div><div>Stroller Friendly Factor: Tough Strollers Only...</div><div><br></div><div>Final Disclaimer: Bring dry clothes and shoes, bug spray, sunscreen&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>(NOT!!), condoms (as always... be safe!!), your grandmother&apos;s underwear&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>(why... we don&apos;t know. Hummm... or is it... you never know?), and your&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>appetite for some fine beers from all over the world!! And... finally...&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>should we remind you... shiggy-socks and/or PI Block.</div><div><br></div><div>Oh... and please don&apos;t forget those beautiful, young female virgins!!</div><div><br></div><div>QUESTIONS: Contact And How&apos;s Her Bush: AndHowsHerBush@yahoo.com</div>', '<div>This week&apos;s trail is at a Great Falls Hasher&apos;s house</div><div>at:</div><div>509 River Bend Road</div><div>Great Falls VA &nbsp;22066".</div>', ''),
