(709, '<div>Since work has made Mr. Ho a ghost the last few weeks he figured he may as well lay a Ghost trail, so here it is.</div><div>Will he be at start...who knows?!? &nbsp;Trail may well be laid by mysterious forces beyond the realm of Hashdom so be prepared.</div><div>Maybe you&apos;ll see him there, or maybe not!</div>', '<div>From Herndon - Take 28 towards Chantilly then take exit for 50 W. &nbsp;Take a right at the 2nd stop light onto Avion Parkway, take a right at second drive then left at rear of building. &nbsp;Look for Ghostly starting signs.</div><div>From Fairfax - Take 50 W to Avion Parkway. &nbsp;Take right and follow directions above</div>', '<div>Picante</div><div>14511 Lee Jackson Memorial Hwy</div><div>Chantilly, VA 20151</div><div><br></div>', '', '3675 Concord Parkway rear of building', 'https://www.google.com/maps/d/edit?mid=z1yVFofA7i34.kGOJ3Ls3YWU8&usp=sharing');
