(719, '<div>Don your ugly holiday sweaters, light up your tutus or wear your naughty Santa outfits and join us for the first anal Festivus Pub Run in Old Town Alexandria. &nbsp;Your hares, I Cunt Hear You and Lush of the Irish, promise to make this a Festivus you won&apos;t soon forget! &nbsp;A Festivus, certainly, for the rest of us!</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Trail is definitely metro or Uber friendly! &nbsp;Celebrate Festivus properly and be safe!!</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Despite this being a bar crawl, because of all of the fun Festivus activities, we&apos;re still charging you $5. So bring your wallets and cash you wanks!</div>', '<div>Start is behind Rock It Grill on N. West St.</div><div><br></div><div>It is a .3 mile walk from the King Street Metro station. &nbsp;Head down King Street and turn left onto N. West St.</div><div><br></div><div>There is a very small parking lot behind the bar. &nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>If you are driving - use your GPS - you know you have one. &nbsp;</div>', 'Rock It Grill<div>1319 King St</div><div>Alexandria, VA 22314</div>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">THE MAIN PRINCIPLES OF FESTIVUS</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">THE FESTIVUS POLE</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">:&nbsp; Is there a tree, you ask?</span>&nbsp; No. Instead, there&apos;s a pole. Requires no decoration. I find tinsel distracting. It&apos;s made from aluminum. Very high strength-to-weight ratio.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Luckily, our own So Happy Hashit will make the perfect Festivus Pole!</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">AIRING OF&nbsp;</span></b><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>GRIEVANCES</b>:&nbsp; "I got a lot of problems with you people! And now you&apos;re gonna hear about it!</font>"<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">Of course, it would not be Festivus without loudly complaining in circle!&nbsp; Our celebration will end with the traditional Airing of Grievances at end circle.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">FEATS OF STRENGTH</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">: &nbsp;Have no fear - there will be a few contests throughout the night and at circle to prove you are, indeed, hasher worthy.&nbsp; Cock fighting anyone?&nbsp; Down Down contest possibly?&nbsp; Fingerrrrrr jousting???</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">FESTIVUS MIRACLES</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">: Who knows?&nbsp; Will Herp stay sober?&nbsp; Will Udder even show up??&nbsp; Will AHHB show up on time with the beer? Will Vaginger pay for her own drinks??&nbsp; Will ATWI be gainfully employed anytime soon?&nbsp; Will Parents Weekend finally not have to call Silver Linings after trail to tell her know he&apos;s a dumbass?</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0.05in 0in 0.0001pt; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;">It&apos;s Festivus - anything is possible!!</span></p>', 'Start is behind Rock It Grill on N. West St.<div>105 N West St<div>Alexandria, VA 22314</div></div>', ''),
(720, '<div>We&apos;ve all gotten some dumb/ugly/crazy S.H.I.T. this X-Mas, so bring some of it to share.</div><div>It&apos;s a BROWN BAG HASH!</div><div>Bring some S.H.I.T. in a bag you don&apos;t want (preferably something itchy/uncomfortable/awesome to wear) because it&apos;s the time for giving. Before trail we will randomly exchange our bags of S.H.I.T. with each other and bring said S.H.I.T.y article with us on trail. Bag of S.H.I.T. required in order to receive another said random bag of S.H.I.T..</div>', '<div>Rt 66 to 286N</div><div>Turn left on FairLakes Pkw</div><div><br></div>', '<div><b>Prelube:</b></div><div>Red Robin</div><div>13056 Fair Lakes Shopping Center, Fairfax, VA 22033</div><div><br></div><div><b>On-On-On:&nbsp;</b></div><div>Red Rocks</div><div>13850 Braddock Rd, Centreville, VA 20121</div>', '', '<div>Behind the shutdown Asian Food Store</div><div>1301 Fair Lakes Shopping Center, Fair Lakes Shopping Center, Fairfax, VA 22033</div>', 'http://maps.google.com/maps?q=13056%20Fair%20Lakes%20Shopping%20Center%2C%20Fairfax%2C%20VA%2022033'),
