(725, 'It&apos;s groundhogs day ladies and wanks. And you know what that means? Good, because I don&apos;t!<div>But I did see this movie once, where Peter Venkman got so drunk, he was able to perfect drunk driving and gopher genocide.</div><div>So, we&apos;re gonna see if we can apply some of these techniques to work on our drinking skills</div>', '<b>From the East or West:</b><div><div style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Get to Route 66</div></div><div style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Take Exit 55B (286 N)</div><div style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Take your first exit onto Fair Lakes Parkway, and go Left at the light</div><div style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Make your second left onto Headquarters Dr</div><div style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;">Find some wankers!</div><div style="height: 327px;"><b style="height: 327px;">From the North (Ashburn for Old Man Busch)<br></b>Take 28 South<br>Turn left onto route 50 (take it East)<br>Turn right onto 286 (go South)<br>Turn right onto Fair Lakes Parkway<br>Make your first left onto Headquarters Dr<br>Find some wankers</div><div style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><b style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><br></b></div>', 'We&apos;ll be prelubing and onononing at TBD.<div>Find us on FB to figure it out</div>', 'It&apos;s snowy, and we may be getting wet (think snowballs, snowtackles, and poorly laid trail!)<div>Bring layers, dry extras, and a can drink attitude.</div>', 'Behind the&nbsp;Residence Inn Fair Lakes Fairfax<div>12815 Fair Lakes Pkwy</div><div>Fairfax, VA 22033</div>', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/12815+Fair+Lakes+Pkwy,+Fairfax,+VA+22033/@38.8622422,-77.386563,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89b6458ca9173065:0x600c7a77963c8752'),
(726, '', '<span style="color: rgb(55, 62, 77); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 13.9636px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);">McLean Metro - Exit metro but use the sky-bridge over 123. Head 1 block east (away from the Tyson&apos;s Corner skyline), make a right on Anderson Rd, pass Lost Dog Caf?, and continue for 3 blocks. Cars can also get into Pimmit hills off Rte. 7 from Magarity Rd (from 495) and Pimmit Dr. (from 66).</span>', 'Lost Dog Cafe<div><span style="color: rgb(55, 62, 77); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);">1690 Anderson Rd McLean, VA 2210216 beers on tap; 189 in bottles or cans.</span></div>', '', 'Casa Fingererereggerere<div><span style="color: rgb(55, 62, 77); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15.36px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);">1808 Anderson RoadFalls Church VA, 22043</span></div>', 'https://www.google.com/maps/@38.8668458,-77.0967355,15z'),
(727, '<span style="color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;">It will be a usual MILF trail so length is questionable, there are no guarantees that everyone will make it back, and I&apos;ll probably run out of flour.</span>', '<span style="color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;">Directions to start:&nbsp;From 66: Take the Vienna metro Rt. 243 exit and go past the off ramps to Metro Parking. At the intersection make a left onto Country Creek Rd then make your next left onto Sutton Rd. Go around the HS and make a right onto Blake Ln followed by a right onto Tipperary Pass. Park along Tipperary Pass or whatever guest spots you can find.</span>', '<span style="color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;">Vienna Inn</span><div style="color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;">120 Maple Avenue E</span></div>', '', '<span style="color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;">2935 Cashel Lane&nbsp;</span><div><span style="color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;">Vienna, VA</span></div>', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/2935+Cashel+Ln,+Vienna,+VA+22181/@38.8779622,-77.287629,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x89b64bfde4242cd3:0x86e4883d768c0dba');
