(728, '<font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">Hummm...</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">Whatever happened to simplicity?</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">Not to date myself, but... I&apos;m dating myself, I remember\nwhen we had to use road atlases to do trail!! You know... those multiple\njurisdictions ones that included "Fairfax County", "Montgomery County", "Prince\nGeorges County", and Washington DC. You got part of Loudoun County, however,\nyou had to go to a Loudoun County atlas to get anything west of Sterling.</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">Oh... and let&apos;s not forget that you had to call PUD-JAM0\nin order to get directions!!</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">Then... internet and Google Maps, Yahoo Groups, Mapquest\nand the like came out along with GPS in autos, cell phone and watches and\nPUD-JAM0 became history.</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">Now... it seems like Facebook has taken over!! Well... I don&apos;t\ngo to Facebook to find out if I&apos;m on the hareline... we DO have a website,\nhowever, the website didn&apos;t list any hares the past two weeks, however, I\nseemed to have been added to both weeks as a hare?</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica;&apos;><font size="3">I was talking to Cama Sutra last week and commented on\nhow nice it was to have her out on So Happy It&apos;s Tuesday trails as often along\nwith Yarben (who recently was added to the "A" list!!). Cama Sutra said... well...\nwhen you have trail out closer to the beltway... it&apos;s not so hard. Cama Sutra... "sorry",\nnot this week!!</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">Okay then... let&apos;s get onto more important\ninformation!!</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Georgia","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;&apos;><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3">\n\n</font><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style=&apos;color: black; font-family: "Bookman Old Style","serif"; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-no-proof: yes;&apos;><font size="3">This week&apos;s trail will\n"START" is at: <b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><font color="#000000" face="Bookman Old Style">"</font></b></font></span><a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/43865+Freedom+Station+Plaza,+Ashburn,+VA+20148/@38.99641,-7